(2, 'C&#7845;p m&#7899;i Ch&#7913;ng minh nh&#226;n d&#226;n t&#7841;i C&#244;ng an c&#7845;p huy&#7879;n', 1, 0, '<p>a) C&#417; quan c&oacute; th&#7849;m quy&#7873;n quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh: C&ocirc;ng an t&#7881;nh H&#432;ng Y&ecirc;n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>b) C&#417; quan ho&#7863;c ng&#432;&#7901;i c&oacute; th&#7849;m quy&#7873;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c u&#7927; quy&#7873;n ho&#7863;c ph&acirc;n c&#7845;p th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n (n&#7871;u c&oacute;): kh&ocirc;ng</p>\r\n\r\n<p>c) C&#417; quan tr&#7921;c ti&#7871;p th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n TTHC: Ph&ograve;ng C&#7843;nh s&aacute;t QLHC v&#7873; TTXH ;C&ocirc;ng an huy&#7879;n, th&agrave;nh ph&#7889;- CA t&#7881;nh H&#432;ng y&ecirc;n.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>d) C&#417; quan ph&#7889;i h&#7907;p (n&#7871;u c&oacute;): Ph&ograve;ng h&#7891; s&#417; nghi&#7879;p v&#7909; (PV27) C&ocirc;ng an t&#7881;nh H&#432;ng Y&ecirc;n.</p>\r\n', '<p><strong>B&#432;&#7899;c 1</strong> - Chu&#7849;n b&#7883; h&#7891; s&#417; theo quy &#273;&#7883;nh c&#7911;a ph&aacute;p lu&#7853;t<br />\r\n<strong>B&#432;&#7899;c 2</strong> - &#272;&#7871;n n&#7897;p h&#7891; s&#417; t&#7841;i tr&#7909; s&#7903; C&ocirc;ng an huy&#7879;n, th&agrave;nh ph&#7889; thu&#7897;c t&#7881;nh H&#432;ng Y&ecirc;n<br />\r\n* C&aacute;n b&#7897; ti&ecirc;&#769;p nh&acirc;&#803;n h&ocirc;&#768; s&#417; ki&ecirc;&#777;m tra ti&#769;nh pha&#769;p ly&#769; va&#768; n&ocirc;&#803;i dung h&ocirc;&#768; s&#417;:<br />\r\n- Tr&#432;&#417;&#768;ng h&#417;&#803;p h&ocirc;&#768; s&#417; &#273;a&#771; &#273;&acirc;&#768;y &#273;u&#777;, h&#417;&#803;p l&ecirc;&#803; thi&#768; h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n l&agrave;m c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng vi&#7879;c sau v&agrave; vi&ecirc;&#769;t gi&acirc;&#769;y bi&ecirc;n nh&#7853;n trao cho ng&#432;&#417;&#768;i n&ocirc;&#803;p:<br />\r\n+ K&ecirc; khai t&#7901; khai c&#7845;p CMND (theo m&#7851;u);<br />\r\n+ In v&acirc;n tay 10 ng&oacute;n v&agrave;o ch&#7881; b&#7843;n, t&#7901; khai (theo m&#7851;u).<br />\r\n- Tr&#432;&#417;&#768;ng h&#417;&#803;p h&ocirc;&#768; s&#417; thi&ecirc;&#769;u, ho&#259;&#803;c kh&ocirc;ng h&#417;&#803;p l&ecirc;&#803; thi&#768; c&aacute;n b&#7897; ti&ecirc;&#769;p nh&acirc;&#803;n h&ocirc;&#768; s&#417; h&#432;&#417;&#769;ng d&acirc;&#771;n &#273;&ecirc;&#777; ng&#432;&#417;&#768;i &#273;&ecirc;&#769;n n&ocirc;&#803;p h&ocirc;&#768; s&#417; la&#768;m la&#803;i cho ki&#803;p th&#7901;i.<br />\r\n* Ph&ograve;ng PC13:<br />\r\n+Ho&agrave;n ch&#7881;nh CMND.<br />\r\n+Tr&#7843; C&ocirc;ng an c&aacute;c huy&#7879;n, th&agrave;nh ph&#7889; c&#7845;p cho nh&acirc;n d&acirc;n s&#7917; d&#7909;ng.<br />\r\n* Th&#417;&#768;i gian ti&ecirc;&#769;p nh&acirc;&#803;n h&ocirc;&#768; s&#417;:<br />\r\nT&#432;&#768; th&#7913; 2 &#273;&#7871;n th&#7913; 6 ha&#768;ng tu&acirc;&#768;n (nga&#768;y l&ecirc;&#771; nghi&#777;) ho&#7863;c theo l&#7883;ch c&#7909; th&#7875; c&#7911;a C&ocirc;ng an c&aacute;c huy&#7879;n, th&agrave;nh ph&#7889; thu&#7897;c t&#7881;nh H&#432;ng Y&ecirc;n<br />\r\n* T&#7841;i &#273;&#7883;a &#273;i&#7875;m c&oacute; t&#7893; c&ocirc;ng t&aacute;c c&#7845;p Ch&#7913;ng minh nh&acirc;n d&acirc;n l&#432;u &#273;&#7897;ng: theo th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o c&#7909; th&#7875; c&#7911;a t&#7893; c&ocirc;ng t&aacute;c.<br />\r\n<strong>B&#432;&#7899;c 3</strong> - Nh&#7853;n CMND: Ng&#432;&#7901;i nh&#7853;n &#273;&#432;a gi&#7845;y bi&ecirc;n nh&#7853;n, c&aacute;n b&#7897; tra&#777; k&#7871;t qu&#7843; ki&ecirc;&#777;m tra va&#768; y&ecirc;u c&acirc;&#768;u ky&#769; nh&acirc;&#803;n, tr&#7843; CMND cho ng&#432;&#417;&#768;i &#273;&ecirc;&#769;n nh&acirc;&#803;n k&#7871;t qu&#7843;.<br />\r\n- &#272;&#7883;a &#273;i&#7875;m nh&#7853;n k&#7871;t qu&#7843;: Nh&#7853;n CMND t&#7841;i tr&#7909; s&#7903; C&ocirc;ng an huy&#7879;n, th&agrave;nh ph&#7889; ho&#7863;c C&ocirc;ng an ph&#432;&#7901;ng, x&atilde;, th&#7883; tr&#7845;n thu&#7897;c t&#7881;nh H&#432;ng Y&ecirc;n.<br />\r\n- Th&#7901;i gian tr&#7843; k&#7871;t qu&#7843;: T&#432;&#768; th&#7913; 2 &#273;&#7871;n th&#7913; 6 ha&#768;ng tu&acirc;&#768;n (nga&#768;y l&ecirc;&#771; nghi&#777;).</p>\r\n', '<p>- N&#7897;p h&#7891; s&#417; tr&#7921;c ti&#7871;p t&#7841;i b&#7897; ph&acirc;n ch&#7913;ng minh C&ocirc;ng an huy&#7879;n, th&agrave;nh ph&#7889;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Nh&#7853;n k&#7871;t qu&#7843; t&#7841;i b&#7897; ph&#7853;n c&#7845;p ch&#7913;ng minh C&ocirc;ng an huy&#7879;n, th&agrave;nh ph&#7889; ho&#7863;c C&ocirc;ng an c&aacute;c x&atilde;, ph&#432;&#7901;ng n&#417;i c&#432; tr&uacute;</p>\r\n', 'C&#225; nh&#226;n', '<p>- Theo quy &#273;&#7883;nh:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>+ &#7902; th&agrave;nh ph&#7889;, th&#7883; x&atilde;: 15 ng&agrave;y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>+ &#7902; khu v&#7921;c kh&aacute;c: 30 ng&agrave;y.</p>\r\n', '<p>C&#7845;p m&#7899;i ch&#7913;ng minh nh&acirc;n d&acirc;n ph&iacute; 3.000&#273;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(Th&ocirc;ng t&#432; s&#7889; 77/2002/TT-BTC ng&agrave;y 10/9/2002 c&#7911;a B&#7897; T&agrave;i ch&iacute;nh Quy &#273;&#7883;nh v&#7873; ch&#7871; &#273;&#7897; thu, n&#7897;p v&agrave; qu&#7843;n l&yacute;, s&#7917; d&#7909;ng l&#7879; ph&iacute; CMND).</p>\r\n', 'Gi&#7845;y CMND', '&#272;&#417;n &#273;&#7873; ngh&#7883; c&#7845;p CMND', 'Cap_moi_Chung_minh_nhan_dan_tai_Cong_an_cap_Huyen.doc', '<p>- S&#7893; h&#7897; kh&#7849;u (HK08)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- &#272;&#417;n &#273;&#7873; ngh&#7883; c&#7845;p CMND (CM3)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- T&#7901; khai CMND (CM4)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Ch&#7881; b&#7843;n (A7)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- &#7842;nh 3 x 4</p>\r\n', '1', '<p>&#272;i&#7873;u ki&#7879;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&#7845;p m&#7899;i CMND g&#7891;m:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>a) C&ocirc;ng d&acirc;n Vi&#7879;t Nam t&#7915; &#273;&#7911; 14 tu&#7893;i tr&#7903; l&ecirc;n, c&#417; s&#7903; &#273;&#7875; t&iacute;nh tu&#7893;i theo ng&agrave;y, th&aacute;ng, n&#259;m sinh ghi trong h&#7897; kh&#7849;u ho&#7863;c gi&#7845;y khai sinh;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>b) C&ocirc;ng d&acirc;n Vi&#7879;t Nam &#273;ang c&#432; tr&uacute; tr&ecirc;n l&atilde;nh th&#7893; Vi&#7879;t Nam: &#273;&#432;&#7907;c hi&#7875;u l&agrave; c&ocirc;ng d&acirc;n &#273;&oacute; &#273;ang sinh s&#7889;ng, l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c, h&#7885;c t&#7853;p... t&#7841;i m&#7897;t &#273;&#7883;a ch&#7881; x&aacute;c &#273;&#7883;nh tr&ecirc;n l&atilde;nh th&#7893; Vi&#7879;t Nam;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>c) Kh&ocirc;ng thu&#7897;c di&#7879;n &#273;&#7889;i t&#432;&#7907;ng t&#7841;m th&#7901;i ch&#432;a &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&#7845;p CMND bao g&#7891;m:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- &#272;ang ch&#7845;p h&agrave;nh l&#7879;nh t&#7841;m giam t&#7841;i tr&#7841;i giam, nh&agrave; t&#7841;m gi&#7919;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- &#272;ang thi h&agrave;nh &aacute;n ph&#7841;t t&ugrave; t&#7841;i tr&#7841;i giam, ph&acirc;n tr&#7841;i qu&#7843;n l&yacute; ph&#7841;m nh&acirc;n thu&#7897;c tr&#7841;i t&#7841;m giam;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- &#272;ang ch&#7845;p h&agrave;nh quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh &#273;&#432;a v&agrave;o c&aacute;c tr&#432;&#7901;ng gi&aacute;o d&#432;&#7905;ng, c&#417; s&#7903; gi&aacute;o d&#7909;c, c&#417; s&#7903; ch&#7919;a b&#7879;nh;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i &#273;ang m&#7855;c b&#7879;nh t&acirc;m th&#7847;n ho&#7863;c b&#7879;nh kh&aacute;c kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; kh&#7843; n&#259;ng &#273;i&#7873;u khi&#7875;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c n&#259;ng l&#7921;c h&agrave;nh vi c&#7911;a b&#7843;n th&acirc;n h&#7885; bao g&#7891;m ng&#432;&#7901;i b&#7883; b&#7879;nh &#273;ang &#273;i&#7873;u tr&#7883; t&#7853;p trung t&#7841;i c&aacute;c b&#7879;nh vi&#7879;n t&acirc;m th&#7847;n, c&#417; s&#7903; y t&#7871; kh&aacute;c. Nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i tuy kh&ocirc;ng &#273;i&#7873;u tr&#7883; t&#7853;p trung nh&#432;ng c&oacute; x&aacute;c nh&#7853;n c&#7911;a c&#417; quan y t&#7871; c&oacute; th&#7849;m quy&#7873;n ch&#7913;ng nh&#7853;n h&#7885; b&#7883; b&#7879;nh kh&ocirc;ng &#273;i&#7873;u khi&#7875;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c n&#259;ng l&#7921;c h&agrave;nh vi th&igrave; c&#361;ng t&#7841;m th&#7901;i ch&#432;a &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&#7845;p CMND.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>d) Ch&#432;a &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&#7845;p CMND theo Ngh&#7883; &#273;&#7883;nh s&#7889; 05/1999/N&#272;-CP c&#7911;a Ch&iacute;nh ph&#7911; v&agrave; gi&#7845;y CMND theo Quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh s&#7889; 143/CP ng&agrave;y 09/8/1976 c&#7911;a H&#7897;i &#273;&#7891;ng Ch&iacute;nh ph&#7911;.</p>\r\n', '<p>- Ngh&#7883; &#273;&#7883;nh s&#7889; 05/1999/N&#272;-CP ng&agrave;y 3/2/1999 c&#7911;a Ch&iacute;nh ph&#7911; v&#7873; CMND. C&oacute; hi&#7879;u l&#7921;c k&#7875; t&#7915; ng&agrave;y 01/5/1999;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Th&ocirc;ng t&#432; s&#7889; 04/1999/TT-BCA (C13) ng&agrave;y 29/4/1999 c&#7911;a B&#7897; C&ocirc;ng an quy &#273;&#7883;nh h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n m&#7897;t s&#7889; quy &#273;&#7883;nh c&#7911;a N&#272; s&#7889; 05/1999/N&#272;-CP ng&agrave;y 3/2/1999 c&#7911;a Ch&iacute;nh ph&#7911; v&#7873; CMND. C&oacute; hi&#7879;u l&#7921;c t&#7915; ng&agrave;y 1/5/1999;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Th&ocirc;ng t&#432; s&#7889; 77/2002/TT-BTC ng&agrave;y 10/9/2002 c&#7911;a B&#7897; T&agrave;i ch&iacute;nh Quy &#273;&#7883;nh v&#7873; ch&#7871; &#273;&#7897; thu, n&#7897;p v&agrave; qu&#7843;n l&yacute;, s&#7917; d&#7909;ng l&#7879; ph&iacute; CMND;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh s&#7889; 998/2001/BCA (C11) ng&agrave;y 10/10/2001 c&#7911;a B&#7897; C&ocirc;ng an v&#7873; vi&#7879;c ban h&agrave;nh c&aacute;c lo&#7841;i bi&#7875;u m&#7851;u s&#7917; d&#7909;ng trong c&ocirc;ng t&aacute;c qu&#7843;n l&yacute; h&agrave;nh ch&iacute;nh v&#7873; TTXH.</p>\r\n', 'cap-moi-chung-minh-nhan-dan-tai-cong-an-cap-huyen', 3, 2),
(3, 'C&#7845;p l&#7841;i Ch&#7913;ng minh nh&#226;n d&#226;n t&#7841;i C&#244;ng an c&#7845;p huy&#7879;n', 1, 0, '<p>a) C&#417; quan c&oacute; th&#7849;m quy&#7873;n quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh: C&ocirc;ng an t&#7881;nh H&#432;ng Y&ecirc;n<br />\r\nb) C&#417; quan ho&#7863;c ng&#432;&#7901;i c&oacute; th&#7849;m quy&#7873;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c u&#7927; quy&#7873;n ho&#7863;c ph&acirc;n c&#7845;p th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n (n&#7871;u c&oacute;): kh&ocirc;ng<br />\r\nc) C&#417; quan tr&#7921;c ti&#7871;p th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n TTHC: Ph&ograve;ng C&#7843;nh s&aacute;t QLHC v&#7873; TTXH ;C&ocirc;ng an huy&#7879;n, th&agrave;nh ph&#7889;- CA t&#7881;nh H&#432;ng y&ecirc;n.<br />\r\nd) C&#417; quan ph&#7889;i h&#7907;p (n&#7871;u c&oacute;): Ph&ograve;ng h&#7891; s&#417; nghi&#7879;p v&#7909; (PV27) C&ocirc;ng an t&#7881;nh H&#432;ng Y&ecirc;n.</p>\r\n', '<p>- B&#432;&#7899;c 1- Chu&#7849;n b&#7883; h&#7891; s&#417; theo quy &#273;&#7883;nh c&#7911;a ph&aacute;p lu&#7853;t<br />\r\nB&#432;&#7899;c 2- &#272;&#7871;n n&#7897;p h&#7891; s&#417; t&#7841;i tr&#7909; s&#7903; C&ocirc;ng an huy&#7879;n, th&agrave;nh ph&#7889; thu&#7897;c t&#7881;nh H&#432;ng Y&ecirc;n<br />\r\n* C&aacute;n b&#7897; ti&ecirc;&#769;p nh&acirc;&#803;n h&ocirc;&#768; s&#417; ki&ecirc;&#777;m tra ti&#769;nh pha&#769;p ly&#769; va&#768; n&ocirc;&#803;i dung h&ocirc;&#768; s&#417;:<br />\r\n- Tr&#432;&#417;&#768;ng h&#417;&#803;p h&ocirc;&#768; s&#417; &#273;a&#771; &#273;&acirc;&#768;y &#273;u&#777;, h&#417;&#803;p l&ecirc;&#803; thi&#768; h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n l&agrave;m c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng vi&#7879;c sau v&agrave; vi&ecirc;&#769;t gi&acirc;&#769;y bi&ecirc;n nh&#7853;n trao cho ng&#432;&#417;&#768;i n&ocirc;&#803;p:<br />\r\n+ K&ecirc; khai t&#7901; khai c&#7845;p CMND (theo m&#7851;u);<br />\r\n+ In v&acirc;n tay 10 ng&oacute;n v&agrave;o ch&#7881; b&#7843;n, t&#7901; khai (theo m&#7851;u).<br />\r\n- Tr&#432;&#417;&#768;ng h&#417;&#803;p h&ocirc;&#768; s&#417; thi&ecirc;&#769;u, ho&#259;&#803;c kh&ocirc;ng h&#417;&#803;p l&ecirc;&#803; thi&#768; c&aacute;n b&#7897; ti&ecirc;&#769;p nh&acirc;&#803;n h&ocirc;&#768; s&#417; h&#432;&#417;&#769;ng d&acirc;&#771;n &#273;&ecirc;&#777; ng&#432;&#417;&#768;i &#273;&ecirc;&#769;n n&ocirc;&#803;p h&ocirc;&#768; s&#417; la&#768;m la&#803;i cho ki&#803;p th&#7901;i.<br />\r\n* Ph&ograve;ng PC13:<br />\r\n+Ho&agrave;n ch&#7881;nh CMND.<br />\r\n+Tr&#7843; C&ocirc;ng an c&aacute;c huy&#7879;n, th&agrave;nh ph&#7889; c&#7845;p cho nh&acirc;n d&acirc;n s&#7917; d&#7909;ng.<br />\r\n* Th&#417;&#768;i gian ti&ecirc;&#769;p nh&acirc;&#803;n h&ocirc;&#768; s&#417;:<br />\r\nT&#432;&#768; th&#7913; 2 &#273;&#7871;n th&#7913; 6 ha&#768;ng tu&acirc;&#768;n (nga&#768;y l&ecirc;&#771; nghi&#777;) ho&#7863;c theo l&#7883;ch c&#7909; th&#7875; c&#7911;a C&ocirc;ng an c&aacute;c huy&#7879;n, th&agrave;nh ph&#7889; thu&#7897;c t&#7881;nh H&#432;ng Y&ecirc;n<br />\r\n* T&#7841;i &#273;&#7883;a &#273;i&#7875;m c&oacute; t&#7893; c&ocirc;ng t&aacute;c c&#7845;p Ch&#7913;ng minh nh&acirc;n d&acirc;n l&#432;u &#273;&#7897;ng: theo th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o c&#7909; th&#7875; c&#7911;a t&#7893; c&ocirc;ng t&aacute;c.<br />\r\nB&#432;&#7899;c 3- Nh&#7853;n CMND: Ng&#432;&#7901;i nh&#7853;n &#273;&#432;a gi&#7845;y bi&ecirc;n nh&#7853;n, c&aacute;n b&#7897; tra&#777; k&#7871;t qu&#7843; ki&ecirc;&#777;m tra va&#768; y&ecirc;u c&acirc;&#768;u ky&#769; nh&acirc;&#803;n, tr&#7843; CMND cho ng&#432;&#417;&#768;i &#273;&ecirc;&#769;n nh&acirc;&#803;n k&#7871;t qu&#7843;.<br />\r\n- &#272;&#7883;a &#273;i&#7875;m nh&#7853;n k&#7871;t qu&#7843;: Nh&#7853;n CMND t&#7841;i tr&#7909; s&#7903; C&ocirc;ng an huy&#7879;n, th&agrave;nh ph&#7889; ho&#7863;c C&ocirc;ng an ph&#432;&#7901;ng, x&atilde;, th&#7883; tr&#7845;n thu&#7897;c t&#7881;nh H&#432;ng Y&ecirc;n.<br />\r\n- Th&#7901;i gian tr&#7843; k&#7871;t qu&#7843;: T&#432;&#768; th&#7913; 2 &#273;&#7871;n th&#7913; 6 ha&#768;ng tu&acirc;&#768;n (nga&#768;y l&ecirc;&#771; nghi&#777;).</p>\r\n', '<p>- N&#7897;p h&#7891; s&#417; tr&#7921;c ti&#7871;p t&#7841;i b&#7897; ph&acirc;n ch&#7913;ng minh C&ocirc;ng an huy&#7879;n, th&agrave;nh ph&#7889;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Nh&#7853;n k&#7871;t qu&#7843; t&#7841;i b&#7897; ph&#7853;n c&#7845;p ch&#7913;ng minh C&ocirc;ng an huy&#7879;n, th&agrave;nh ph&#7889; ho&#7863;c C&ocirc;ng an c&aacute;c x&atilde;, ph&#432;&#7901;ng n&#417;i c&#432; tr&uacute;</p>\r\n', 'C&#225; nh&#226;n', '<p>- Theo quy &#273;&#7883;nh:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>+&#7902; th&agrave;nh ph&#7889;, th&#7883; x&atilde;: 15 ng&agrave;y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>+ &#7902; khu v&#7921;c kh&aacute;c: 30 ng&agrave;y.</p>\r\n', '<p>C&#7845;p m&#7899;i ch&#7913;ng minh nh&acirc;n d&acirc;n ph&iacute; 3.000&#273;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(Th&ocirc;ng t&#432; s&#7889; 77/2002/TT-BTC ng&agrave;y 10/9/2002 c&#7911;a B&#7897; T&agrave;i ch&iacute;nh Quy &#273;&#7883;nh v&#7873; ch&#7871; &#273;&#7897; thu, n&#7897;p v&agrave; qu&#7843;n l&yacute;, s&#7917; d&#7909;ng l&#7879; ph&iacute; CMND).</p>\r\n', 'Gi&#7845;y CMND', 'C&#7845;p l&#7841;i Ch&#7913;ng minh nh&#226;n d&#226;n t&#7841;i C&#244;ng an c&#7845;p huy&#7879;n', 'Cap_lai_Chung_minh_nhan_dan_tai_Cong_an_cap_huyen.doc', '<p>- S&#7893; h&#7897; kh&#7849;u (HK08)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- &#272;&#417;n &#273;&#7873; ngh&#7883; c&#7845;p CMND (CM 3)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- T&#7901; khai CMND (CM4)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Ch&#7881; b&#7843;n (A7)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- &#7842;nh 3 x 4</p>\r\n', '1', '<p>&#272;i&#7873;u ki&#7879;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&#7845;p l&#7841;i CMND g&#7891;m:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>a) C&ocirc;ng d&acirc;n Vi&#7879;t Nam t&#7915; &#273;&#7911; 14 tu&#7893;i tr&#7903; l&ecirc;n, c&#417; s&#7903; &#273;&#7875; t&iacute;nh tu&#7893;i theo ng&agrave;y, th&aacute;ng, n&#259;m sinh ghi trong h&#7897; kh&#7849;u ho&#7863;c gi&#7845;y khai sinh;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>b) C&ocirc;ng d&acirc;n Vi&#7879;t Nam &#273;ang c&#432; tr&uacute; tr&ecirc;n l&atilde;nh th&#7893; Vi&#7879;t Nam: &#273;&#432;&#7907;c hi&#7875;u l&agrave; c&ocirc;ng d&acirc;n &#273;&oacute; &#273;ang sinh s&#7889;ng, l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c, h&#7885;c t&#7853;p... t&#7841;i m&#7897;t &#273;&#7883;a ch&#7881; x&aacute;c &#273;&#7883;nh tr&ecirc;n l&atilde;nh th&#7893; Vi&#7879;t Nam;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>c) Kh&ocirc;ng thu&#7897;c di&#7879;n &#273;&#7889;i t&#432;&#7907;ng t&#7841;m th&#7901;i ch&#432;a &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&#7845;p CMND bao g&#7891;m:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- &#272;ang ch&#7845;p h&agrave;nh l&#7879;nh t&#7841;m giam t&#7841;i tr&#7841;i giam, nh&agrave; t&#7841;m gi&#7919;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- &#272;ang thi h&agrave;nh &aacute;n ph&#7841;t t&ugrave; t&#7841;i tr&#7841;i giam, ph&acirc;n tr&#7841;i qu&#7843;n l&yacute; ph&#7841;m nh&acirc;n thu&#7897;c tr&#7841;i t&#7841;m giam;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- &#272;ang ch&#7845;p h&agrave;nh quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh &#273;&#432;a v&agrave;o c&aacute;c tr&#432;&#7901;ng gi&aacute;o d&#432;&#7905;ng, c&#417; s&#7903; gi&aacute;o d&#7909;c, c&#417; s&#7903; ch&#7919;a b&#7879;nh;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i &#273;ang m&#7855;c b&#7879;nh t&acirc;m th&#7847;n ho&#7863;c b&#7879;nh kh&aacute;c kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; kh&#7843; n&#259;ng &#273;i&#7873;u khi&#7875;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c n&#259;ng l&#7921;c h&agrave;nh vi c&#7911;a b&#7843;n th&acirc;n h&#7885; bao g&#7891;m ng&#432;&#7901;i b&#7883; b&#7879;nh &#273;ang &#273;i&#7873;u tr&#7883; t&#7853;p trung t&#7841;i c&aacute;c b&#7879;nh vi&#7879;n t&acirc;m th&#7847;n, c&#417; s&#7903; y t&#7871; kh&aacute;c. Nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i tuy kh&ocirc;ng &#273;i&#7873;u tr&#7883; t&#7853;p trung nh&#432;ng c&oacute; x&aacute;c nh&#7853;n c&#7911;a c&#417; quan y t&#7871; c&oacute; th&#7849;m quy&#7873;n ch&#7913;ng nh&#7853;n h&#7885; b&#7883; b&#7879;nh kh&ocirc;ng &#273;i&#7873;u khi&#7875;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c n&#259;ng l&#7921;c h&agrave;nh vi th&igrave; c&#361;ng t&#7841;m th&#7901;i ch&#432;a &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&#7845;p CMND.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>d) &#272;&atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&#7845;p CMND theo Ngh&#7883; &#273;&#7883;nh s&#7889; 05/1999/N&#272;-CP c&#7911;a Ch&iacute;nh ph&#7911; v&agrave; gi&#7845;y CMND theo Quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh s&#7889; 143/CP ng&agrave;y 09/8/1976 c&#7911;a H&#7897;i &#273;&#7891;ng Ch&iacute;nh ph&#7911;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>e) B&#7883; m&#7845;t ch&#7913;ng minh nh&acirc;n d&acirc;n.</p>\r\n', '<p>- Ngh&#7883; &#273;&#7883;nh s&#7889; 05/1999/N&#272;-CP ng&agrave;y 3/2/1999 c&#7911;a Ch&iacute;nh ph&#7911; v&#7873; CMND. C&oacute; hi&#7879;u l&#7921;c k&#7875; t&#7915; ng&agrave;y 01/5/1999;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Ngh&#7883; &#273;&#7883;nh s&#7889; 34/2008/N&#272;-CP quy &#273;&#7883;nh v&#7873; tuy&#7875;n d&#7909;ng v&agrave; qu&#7843;n l&yacute; ng&#432;&#7901;i n&#432;&#7899;c ngo&agrave;i l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c t&#7841;i Vi&#7879;t Nam;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Th&ocirc;ng t&#432; s&#7889; 04/1999/TT-BCA (C13) ng&agrave;y 29/4/1999 c&#7911;a B&#7897; C&ocirc;ng an quy &#273;&#7883;nh h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n m&#7897;t s&#7889; quy &#273;&#7883;nh c&#7911;a N&#272; s&#7889; 05/1999/N&#272;-CP ng&agrave;y 3/2/1999 c&#7911;a Ch&iacute;nh ph&#7911; v&#7873; CMND. C&oacute; hi&#7879;u l&#7921;c t&#7915; ng&agrave;y 1/5/1999;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Th&ocirc;ng t&#432; s&#7889; 77/2002/TT-BTC ng&agrave;y 10/9/2002 c&#7911;a B&#7897; T&agrave;i ch&iacute;nh Quy &#273;&#7883;nh v&#7873; ch&#7871; &#273;&#7897; thu, n&#7897;p v&agrave; qu&#7843;n l&yacute;, s&#7917; d&#7909;ng l&#7879; ph&iacute; CMND;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh s&#7889; 998/2001/BCA (C11) ng&agrave;y 10/10/2001 c&#7911;a B&#7897; C&ocirc;ng an v&#7873; vi&#7879;c ban h&agrave;nh c&aacute;c lo&#7841;i bi&#7875;u m&#7851;u s&#7917; d&#7909;ng trong c&ocirc;ng t&aacute;c qu&#7843;n l&yacute; h&agrave;nh ch&iacute;nh v&#7873; TTXH.</p>\r\n', 'cap-lai-chung-minh-nhan-dan-tai-cong-an-cap-huyen', 3, 2),
(4, 'C&#7845;p th&#7867; t&#7841;m tr&#250; cho ng&#432;&#7901;i n&#432;&#7899;c ngo&#224;i t&#7841;m tr&#250; &#7903; Vi&#7879;t Nam t&#7841;i C&#244;ng an c&#7845;p t&#7881;nh', 1, 0, '<p>a) C&#417; quan c&oacute; th&#7849;m quy&#7873;n quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh: Ph&ograve;ng PA39- C&ocirc;ng an t&#7881;nh H&#432;ng Y&ecirc;n.<br />\r\nb) C&#417; quan ho&#7863;c ng&#432;&#7901;i c&oacute; th&#7849;m quy&#7873;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c u&#7927; quy&#7873;n ho&#7863;c ph&acirc;n c&#7845;p th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n (n&#7871;u c&oacute;): Kh&ocirc;ng.<br />\r\nc) C&#417; quan tr&#7921;c ti&#7871;p th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n TTHC: t&#7841;i &#272;&#7897;i Qu&#7843;n l&yacute; xu&#7845;t nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh- Ph&ograve;ng PA39- C&ocirc;ng an t&#7881;nh H&#432;ng Y&ecirc;n.<br />\r\nd) C&#417; quan ph&#7889;i h&#7907;p (n&#7871;u c&oacute;): Kh&ocirc;ng</p>\r\n', '<p>B&#432;&#7899;c 1- Chu&#7849;n b&#7883; h&#7891; s&#417; theo quy &#273;&#7883;nh c&#7911;a ph&aacute;p lu&#7853;t<br />\r\nB&#432;&#7899;c 2- Ng&#432;&#7901;i n&#432;&#7899;c ngo&agrave;i xin c&#7845;p th&#7867; t&#7841;m tr&uacute; ph&#7843;i th&ocirc;ng qua c&#417; quan, t&#7893; ch&#7913;c, c&aacute; nh&acirc;n m&#7901;i, b&#7843;o l&atilde;nh &#273;&#7875; l&agrave;m th&#7911; t&#7909;c v&#7899;i &#272;&#7897;i Qu&#7843;n l&yacute; xu&#7845;t nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh- Ph&ograve;ng PA39- C&ocirc;ng an t&#7881;nh H&#432;ng Y&ecirc;n.<br />\r\nC&#417; quan, t&#7893; ch&#7913;c, c&aacute; nh&acirc;n m&#7901;i, b&#7843;o l&atilde;nh ng&#432;&#7901;i n&#432;&#7899;c ngo&agrave;i g&#7917;i h&#7891; s&#417; t&#7899;i &#272;&#7897;i Qu&#7843;n l&yacute; xu&#7845;t nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh- Ph&ograve;ng PA39- C&ocirc;ng an t&#7881;nh H&#432;ng Y&ecirc;n.<br />\r\n* C&aacute;n b&#7897; qu&#7843;n l&yacute; xu&#7845;t nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh ti&ecirc;&#769;p nh&acirc;&#803;n h&ocirc;&#768; s&#417; ki&ecirc;&#777;m tra ti&#769;nh pha&#769;p ly&#769; va&#768; n&ocirc;&#803;i dung h&ocirc;&#768; s&#417;:<br />\r\n- Tr&#432;&#417;&#768;ng h&#417;&#803;p h&ocirc;&#768; s&#417; &#273;a&#771; &#273;&acirc;&#768;y &#273;u&#777;, h&#417;&#803;p l&ecirc;&#803; thi&#768; vi&ecirc;&#769;t gi&acirc;&#769;y bi&ecirc;n nh&#7853;n trao cho ng&#432;&#417;&#768;i n&#7897;p h&#7891; s&#417;.<br />\r\n- Tr&#432;&#417;&#768;ng h&#417;&#803;p h&ocirc;&#768; s&#417; thi&ecirc;&#769;u, ho&#259;&#803;c kh&ocirc;ng h&#417;&#803;p l&ecirc;&#803; thi&#768; c&aacute;n b&#7897; ti&ecirc;&#769;p nh&acirc;&#803;n h&ocirc;&#768; s&#417; h&#432;&#417;&#769;ng d&acirc;&#771;n &#273;&ecirc;&#777; ng&#432;&#417;&#768;i &#273;&ecirc;&#769;n n&ocirc;&#803;p h&ocirc;&#768; s&#417; la&#768;m la&#803;i cho ki&#803;p th&#417;&#768;i<br />\r\n* Th&#417;&#768;i gian ti&ecirc;&#769;p nh&acirc;&#803;n h&ocirc;&#768; s&#417;: T&#432;&#768; th&#7913; 2 &#273;&#7871;n th&#7913; 7 ha&#768;ng tu&acirc;&#768;n (nga&#768;y l&ecirc;&#771; nghi&#777;).<br />\r\nB&#432;&#7899;c 3- Nh&#7853;n th&#7867; t&#7841;m tr&uacute; t&#7841;i B&#7897; ph&#7853;n ti&#7871;p nh&#7853;n v&agrave; tr&#7843; k&#7871;t qu&#7843; t&#7841;i &#272;&#7897;i Qu&#7843;n l&yacute; xu&#7845;t nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh- Ph&ograve;ng PA39- C&ocirc;ng an t&#7881;nh H&#432;ng Y&ecirc;n :<br />\r\n- Ng&#432;&#7901;i nh&#7853;n &#273;&#432;a gi&#7845;y bi&ecirc;n nh&#7853;n &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7889;i chi&#7871;u. N&#7897;p l&#7879; ph&iacute; cho c&aacute;n b&#7897; thu l&#7879; ph&iacute;. C&aacute;n b&#7897; thu l&#7879; ph&iacute; nh&#7853;n ti&#7873;n, vi&#7871;t bi&ecirc;n lai thu ti&#7873;n v&agrave; giao gi&#7845;y bi&ecirc;n nh&#7853;n c&ugrave;ng bi&ecirc;n lai thu ti&#7873;n cho ng&#432;&#7901;i n&#7897;p h&#7891; s&#417;. C&aacute;n b&#7897; tra&#777; k&#7871;t qu&#7843; ki&ecirc;&#777;m tra va&#768; y&ecirc;u c&acirc;&#768;u ky&#769; nh&acirc;&#803;n, tr&#7843; th&#7867; t&#7841;m tr&uacute; cho ng&#432;&#417;&#768;i &#273;&ecirc;&#769;n nh&acirc;&#803;n k&#7871;t qu&#7843;.<br />\r\n*Th&#7901;i gian tr&#7843; k&#7871;t qu&#7843;: T&#432;&#768; th&#7913; 2 &#273;&#7871;n th&#7913; 7 ha&#768;ng tu&acirc;&#768;n (nga&#768;y l&ecirc;&#771; nghi&#777;).</p>\r\n', '<p>Tr&#7921;c ti&#7871;p t&#7841;i tr&#7909; s&#7903; &#272;&#7897;i Qu&#7843;n l&yacute; xu&#7845;t nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh- Ph&ograve;ng PA39- C&ocirc;ng an t&#7881;nh H&#432;ng Y&ecirc;n</p>\r\n', 'C&#225; nh&#226;n/T&#7893; ch&#7913;c', '<p>Kh&ocirc;ng qu&aacute; 05 ng&agrave;y l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c k&#7875; t&#7915; ng&agrave;y nh&#7853;n &#273;&#7911; h&#7891; s&#417;.</p>\r\n', '<p>- Th&#7867; c&oacute; gi&aacute; tr&#7883; &#273;&#7871;n 1 n&#259;m: 60 USD</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Th&#7867; c&oacute; gi&aacute; tr&#7883; tr&ecirc;n 1 n&#259;m &#273;&#7871;n 2 n&#259;m: 80 USD</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Th&#7867; c&oacute; gi&aacute; tr&#7883; tr&ecirc;n 2 n&#259;m &#273;&#7871;n 3 n&#259;m: 100 USD</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(Th&ocirc;ng t&#432; s&#7889; 66/2009/TT-BTC ng&agrave;y 30/3/2009 c&#7911;a B&#7897; tr&#432;&#7903;ng B&#7897; T&agrave;i ch&iacute;nh ban h&agrave;nh quy &#273;&#7883;nh ch&#7871; &#273;&#7897; thu, n&#7897;p, qu&#7843;n l&yacute; v&agrave; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng l&#7879; ph&iacute; c&#7845;p h&#7897; chi&#7871;u, th&#7883; th&#7921;c, gi&#7845;y t&#7901; v&#7873; nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh, xu&#7845;t c&#7843;nh, qu&aacute; c&#7843;nh v&agrave; c&#432; tr&uacute; t&#7841;i Vi&#7879;t Nam)</p>\r\n', 'Th&#7867; t&#7841;m tr&#250;', 'C&#7845;p th&#7867; t&#7841;m tr&#250; cho ng&#432;&#7901;i n&#432;&#7899;c ngo&#224;i t&#7841;m tr&#250; &#7903; Vi&#7879;t Nam t&#7841;i C&#244;ng an c&#7845;p t&#7881;nh', 'Cap_the_tam_tru_cho_nguoi_nuoc_ngoai_tam_tru_o_Viet_Nam_tai_Cong_an_cap_tinh.doc', '<p>- V&#259;n b&#7843;n &#273;&#7873; ngh&#7883; c&#7911;a c&#417; quan, t&#7893; ch&#7913;c, c&aacute; nh&acirc;n m&#7901;i, b&#7843;o l&atilde;nh;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 01 t&#7901; khai v&#7873; th&ocirc;ng tin v&#7873; ng&#432;&#7901;i n&#432;&#7899;c ngo&agrave;i xin t&#7841;m tr&uacute;, c&oacute; d&aacute;n &#7843;nh v&agrave; &#273;&oacute;ng d&#7845;u gi&aacute;p lai c&#7911;a c&#417; quan, t&#7893; ch&#7913;c;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 02 &#7843;nh c&#7905; 3 x4 cm;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 01 b&#7843;n ch&#7909;p h&#7897; chi&#7871;u, th&#7883; th&#7921;c c&ograve;n gi&aacute; tr&#7883;, phi&#7871;u xu&#7845;t nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh (mang b&#7843;n ch&iacute;nh &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7889;i chi&#7871;u);</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 01 b&#7843;n sao ho&#7863;c b&#7843;n pho to (mang b&#7843;n ch&iacute;nh &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7889;i chi&#7871;u) gi&#7845;y t&#7901; ch&#7913;ng minh m&#7909;c &#273;&iacute;ch &#7903; l&#7841;i Vi&#7879;t Nam (tu&#7923; tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p c&#7909; th&#7875; n&#7897;p gi&#7845;y t&#7901; th&iacute;ch h&#7907;p: Gi&#7845;y ph&eacute;p &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;, gi&#7845;y ph&eacute;p th&agrave;nh l&#7853;p doanh nghi&#7879;p, gi&#7845;y ph&eacute;p lao &#273;&#7897;ng, gi&#7845;y x&aacute;c nh&#7853;n th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n h&#7897;i &#273;&#7891;ng qu&#7843;n tr&#7883;, gi&#7845;y ph&eacute;p th&agrave;nh l&#7853;p v&#259;n ph&ograve;ng &#273;&#7841;i di&#7879;n, gi&#7845;y &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; k&#7871;t h&ocirc;n, khai sinh...).</p>\r\n', '1', '<p>- C&oacute; th&#7901;i gian t&#7841;m tr&uacute; t&#7841;i Vi&#7879;t Nam t&#7915; 01 n&#259;m tr&#7903; l&ecirc;n;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- H&#7897; chi&#7871;u c&ograve;n th&#7901;i h&#7841;n t&#7915; 01 n&#259;m tr&#7903; l&ecirc;n.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(Ph&aacute;p l&#7879;nh s&#7889; 24/2000/PL-UBTVQH10 ng&agrave;y 28/4/2000 v&#7873; nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh, xu&#7845;t c&#7843;nh, c&#432; tr&uacute; c&#7911;a ng&#432;&#7901;i n&#432;&#7899;c ngo&agrave;i t&#7841;i Vi&#7879;t Nam)</p>\r\n', '<p>- Ph&aacute;p l&#7879;nh s&#7889; 24/2000/PL-UBTVQH10 ng&agrave;y 28/4/2000 v&#7873; nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh, xu&#7845;t c&#7843;nh, c&#432; tr&uacute; c&#7911;a ng&#432;&#7901;i n&#432;&#7899;c ngo&agrave;i t&#7841;i Vi&#7879;t Nam;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Ngh&#7883; &#273;&#7883;nh s&#7889; 21/2001/N&#272;-CP ng&agrave;y 28/5/2001 c&#7911;a Ch&iacute;nh ph&#7911; quy &#273;&#7883;nh chi ti&#7871;t thi h&agrave;nh Ph&aacute;p l&#7879;nh Nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh, xu&#7845;t c&#7843;nh, c&#432; tr&uacute; c&#7911;a ng&#432;&#7901;i n&#432;&#7899;c ngo&agrave;i t&#7841;i Vi&#7879;t Nam;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Th&ocirc;ng t&#432; s&#7889; 66/2009/TT-BTC ng&agrave;y 30/3/2009 c&#7911;a B&#7897; tr&#432;&#7903;ng B&#7897; T&agrave;i ch&iacute;nh ban h&agrave;nh quy &#273;&#7883;nh ch&#7871; &#273;&#7897; thu, n&#7897;p, qu&#7843;n l&yacute; v&agrave; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng l&#7879; ph&iacute; c&#7845;p h&#7897; chi&#7871;u, th&#7883; th&#7921;c, gi&#7845;y t&#7901; v&#7873; nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh, xu&#7845;t c&#7843;nh, qu&aacute; c&#7843;nh v&agrave; c&#432; tr&uacute; t&#7841;i Vi&#7879;t Nam;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Th&ocirc;ng t&#432; li&ecirc;n t&#7883;ch s&#7889; 04/2002/TTLT-BCA-BNG ng&agrave;y 29/01/2002 h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n Ngh&#7883; &#273;&#7883;nh s&#7889; 21/2001/N&#272;-CP ng&agrave;y 28/5/2001 c&#7911;a Ch&iacute;nh ph&#7911; quy &#273;&#7883;nh chi ti&#7871;t thi h&agrave;nh Ph&aacute;p l&#7879;nh Nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh, xu&#7845;t c&#7843;nh, c&#432; tr&uacute; c&#7911;a ng&#432;&#7901;i n&#432;&#7899;c ngo&agrave;i t&#7841;i Vi&#7879;t Nam;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Th&ocirc;ng t&#432; li&ecirc;n t&#7883;ch s&#7889; 01/2007/TTLT-BCA-BNG ng&agrave;y 30/01/2007 s&#7917;a &#273;&#7893;i b&#7893; sung m&#7897;t s&#7889; &#273;i&#7873;u c&#7911;a Th&ocirc;ng t&#432; li&ecirc;n t&#7883;ch s&#7889; 04/2002/TTLT-BCA-BNG ng&agrave;y 29/01/2002.</p>\r\n', 'cap-the-tam-tru-cho-nguoi-nuoc-ngoai-tam-tru-o-viet-nam-tai-cong-an-cap-tinh', 4, 3),
(5, 'S&#7917;a &#273;&#7893;i h&#7897; chi&#7871;u ph&#7893; th&#244;ng t&#7841;i C&#244;ng an c&#7845;p t&#7881;nh', 1, 0, '<p>a) C&#417; quan c&oacute; th&#7849;m quy&#7873;n quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh: C&#7909;c Qu&#7843;n l&yacute; xu&#7845;t nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh, B&#7897; C&ocirc;ng an<br />\r\nb) C&#417; quan ho&#7863;c ng&#432;&#7901;i c&oacute; th&#7849;m quy&#7873;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c u&#7927; quy&#7873;n ho&#7863;c ph&acirc;n c&#7845;p th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n (n&#7871;u c&oacute;): Kh&ocirc;ng<br />\r\nc) C&#417; quan tr&#7921;c ti&#7871;p th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n TTHC: t&#7841;i &#272;&#7897;i Qu&#7843;n l&yacute; xu&#7845;t nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh- Ph&ograve;ng PA39- C&ocirc;ng an t&#7881;nh H&#432;ng Y&ecirc;n.<br />\r\nc) C&#417; quan ph&#7889;i h&#7907;p (n&#7871;u c&oacute;): Kh&ocirc;ng</p>\r\n', '<p>B&#432;&#7899;c 1- Chu&#7849;n b&#7883; h&#7891; s&#417; theo quy &#273;&#7883;nh c&#7911;a ph&aacute;p lu&#7853;t<br />\r\nB&#432;&#7899;c 2- N&#7897;p h&#7891; s&#417; &#273;&#7873; ngh&#7883; s&#7917;a &#273;&#7893;i h&#7897; chi&#7871;u t&#7841;i B&#7897; ph&#7853;n ti&#7871;p nh&#7853;n v&agrave; tr&#7843; k&#7871;t qu&#7843; t&#7841;i &#272;&#7897;i Qu&#7843;n l&yacute; xu&#7845;t nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh- Ph&ograve;ng PA39- C&ocirc;ng an t&#7881;nh H&#432;ng Y&ecirc;n theo m&#7897;t trong 3 c&aacute;ch sau &#273;&acirc;y:<br />\r\n- Tr&#7921;c ti&#7871;p n&#7897;p h&#7891; s&#417;:<br />\r\nT&#7901; khai kh&ocirc;ng ph&#7843;i x&aacute;c nh&#7853;n c&#7911;a C&ocirc;ng an x&atilde;, ph&#432;&#7901;ng, th&#7883; tr&#7845;n n&#417;i th&#432;&#7901;ng tr&uacute; ho&#7863;c t&#7841;m tr&uacute;. Khi &#273;&#7871;n n&#7897;p h&#7891; s&#417; ph&#7843;i xu&#7845;t tr&igrave;nh ch&#7913;ng minh nh&acirc;n d&acirc;n &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7889;i chi&#7871;u.<br />\r\nRi&ecirc;ng &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p t&#7841;m tr&uacute;, khi &#273;&#7871;n n&#7897;p h&#7891; s&#417; c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i xu&#7845;t tr&igrave;nh &quot;Gi&#7845;y ch&#7913;ng nh&#7853;n t&#7841;m tr&uacute;&quot;; n&#7871;u kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; &quot;Gi&#7845;y ch&#7913;ng nh&#7853;n t&#7841;m tr&uacute;&quot; th&igrave; ph&#7843;i xin x&aacute;c nh&#7853;n c&#7911;a C&ocirc;ng an x&atilde;, ph&#432;&#7901;ng, th&#7883; tr&#7845;n n&#417;i t&#7841;m tr&uacute;.<br />\r\n- &#7910;y th&aacute;c cho c&#417; quan, t&#7893; ch&#7913;c c&oacute; t&#432; c&aacute;ch ph&aacute;p nh&acirc;n n&#7897;p h&#7891; s&#417;:<br />\r\nNg&#432;&#7901;i &#7911;y th&aacute;c khai v&agrave; k&yacute; t&ecirc;n v&agrave;o t&#7901; khai &#273;&#7873; ngh&#7883; c&#7845;p, s&#7917;a &#273;&#7893;i h&#7897; chi&#7871;u theo m&#7851;u quy &#273;&#7883;nh, c&oacute; d&#7845;u gi&aacute;p lai &#7843;nh v&agrave; x&aacute;c nh&#7853;n c&#7911;a Th&#7911; tr&#432;&#7903;ng c&#417; quan, t&#7893; ch&#7913;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#7911;y th&aacute;c.<br />\r\nC&#417; quan, t&#7893; ch&#7913;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#7911;y th&aacute;c c&oacute; c&ocirc;ng v&#259;n g&#7917;i C&ocirc;ng an t&#7881;nh, &#273;&#7873; ngh&#7883; gi&#7843;i quy&#7871;t. N&#7871;u &#273;&#7873; ngh&#7883; gi&#7843;i quy&#7871;t cho nhi&#7873;u ng&#432;&#7901;i th&igrave; ph&#7843;i k&egrave;m danh s&aacute;ch nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i &#7911;y th&aacute;c, c&oacute; ch&#7919; k&yacute;, &#273;&oacute;ng d&#7845;u c&#7911;a Th&#7911; tr&#432;&#7903;ng c&#417; quan, t&#7893; ch&#7913;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#7911;y th&aacute;c.<br />\r\nC&aacute;n b&#7897;, nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n c&#7911;a c&#417; quan, t&#7893; ch&#7913;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#7911;y th&aacute;c khi n&#7897;p h&#7891; s&#417; &#273;&#7873; ngh&#7883; c&#7845;p, s&#7917;a &#273;&#7893;i h&#7897; chi&#7871;u c&#7911;a ng&#432;&#7901;i &#7911;y th&aacute;c ph&#7843;i xu&#7845;t tr&igrave;nh gi&#7845;y gi&#7899;i thi&#7879;u c&#7911;a c&#417; quan, t&#7893; ch&#7913;c, ch&#7913;ng minh nh&acirc;n d&acirc;n c&#7911;a b&#7843;n th&acirc;n v&agrave; c&#7911;a ng&#432;&#7901;i &#7911;y th&aacute;c &#273;&#7875; ki&#7875;m tra, &#273;&#7889;i chi&#7871;u.<br />\r\n- G&#7917;i h&#7891; s&#417; v&agrave; &#273;&#7873; ngh&#7883; nh&#7853;n k&#7871;t qu&#7843; qua &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng b&#432;u &#273;i&#7879;n:<br />\r\nT&#7901; khai ph&#7843;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c C&ocirc;ng an x&atilde;, ph&#432;&#7901;ng, th&#7883; tr&#7845;n n&#417;i th&#432;&#7901;ng tr&uacute; ho&#7863;c t&#7841;m tr&uacute; x&aacute;c nh&#7853;n v&agrave; &#273;&oacute;ng d&#7845;u gi&aacute;p lai &#7843;nh k&egrave;m theo b&#7843;n photocopy ch&#7913;ng minh nh&acirc;n d&acirc;n.<br />\r\n&#272;&#7883;a &#273;i&#7875;m, c&aacute;ch th&#7913;c g&#7917;i h&#7891; s&#417; qua &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng b&#432;u &#273;i&#7879;n th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n theo h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n c&#7911;a T&#7853;p &#273;o&agrave;n B&#432;u ch&iacute;nh vi&#7877;n th&ocirc;ng Vi&#7879;t Nam.<br />\r\n* C&aacute;n b&#7897; qu&#7843;n l&yacute; xu&#7845;t nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh ti&ecirc;&#769;p nh&acirc;&#803;n h&ocirc;&#768; s&#417; ki&ecirc;&#777;m tra ti&#769;nh pha&#769;p ly&#769; va&#768; n&ocirc;&#803;i dung h&ocirc;&#768; s&#417;:<br />\r\n- Tr&#432;&#417;&#768;ng h&#417;&#803;p h&ocirc;&#768; s&#417; &#273;a&#771; &#273;&acirc;&#768;y &#273;u&#777;, h&#417;&#803;p l&ecirc;&#803; thi&#768; vi&ecirc;&#769;t gi&acirc;&#769;y bi&ecirc;n nh&#7853;n trao cho ng&#432;&#417;&#768;i n&ocirc;&#803;p v&agrave; y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u n&#7897;p l&#7879; ph&iacute; cho c&aacute;n b&#7897; thu l&#7879; ph&iacute;. C&aacute;n b&#7897; thu l&#7879; ph&iacute; nh&#7853;n ti&#7873;n, vi&#7871;t bi&ecirc;n lai thu ti&#7873;n v&agrave; giao gi&#7845;y bi&ecirc;n nh&#7853;n c&ugrave;ng bi&ecirc;n lai thu ti&#7873;n cho ng&#432;&#7901;i n&#7897;p h&#7891; s&#417;.<br />\r\n- Tr&#432;&#417;&#768;ng h&#417;&#803;p h&ocirc;&#768; s&#417; thi&ecirc;&#769;u, ho&#259;&#803;c kh&ocirc;ng h&#417;&#803;p l&ecirc;&#803; thi&#768; c&aacute;n b&#7897; ti&ecirc;&#769;p nh&acirc;&#803;n h&ocirc;&#768; s&#417; h&#432;&#417;&#769;ng d&acirc;&#771;n &#273;&ecirc;&#777; ng&#432;&#417;&#768;i &#273;&ecirc;&#769;n n&ocirc;&#803;p h&ocirc;&#768; s&#417; la&#768;m la&#803;i cho ki&#803;p th&#417;&#768;i<br />\r\n* Th&#417;&#768;i gian ti&ecirc;&#769;p nh&acirc;&#803;n h&ocirc;&#768; s&#417;: T&#432;&#768; th&#7913; 2 &#273;&#7871;n th&#7913; 7 ha&#768;ng tu&acirc;&#768;n (nga&#768;y l&ecirc;&#771; nghi&#777;).<br />\r\nB&#432;&#7899;c 3- Nh&#7853;n h&#7897; chi&#7871;u t&#7841;i t&#7841;i B&#7897; ph&#7853;n ti&#7871;p nh&#7853;n v&agrave; tr&#7843; k&#7871;t qu&#7843; t&#7841;i &#272;&#7897;i Qu&#7843;n l&yacute; xu&#7845;t nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh- Ph&ograve;ng PA39- C&ocirc;ng an t&#7881;nh H&#432;ng Y&ecirc;n:<br />\r\n- Ng&#432;&#7901;i tr&#7921;c ti&#7871;p nh&#7853;n k&#7871;t qu&#7843; &#273;&#432;a gi&#7845;y bi&ecirc;n nh&#7853;n, bi&ecirc;n lai thu ti&#7873;n v&agrave; xu&#7845;t tr&igrave;nh ch&#7913;ng minh nh&acirc;n d&acirc;n &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7889;i chi&#7871;u. C&aacute;n b&#7897;, nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n c&#7911;a c&#417; quan, t&#7893; ch&#7913;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#7911;y th&aacute;c khi nh&#7853;n h&#7897; chi&#7871;u c&#7911;a ng&#432;&#7901;i &#7911;y th&aacute;c ph&#7843;i &#273;&#432;a gi&#7845;y bi&ecirc;n nh&#7853;n, xu&#7845;t tr&igrave;nh gi&#7845;y gi&#7899;i thi&#7879;u c&#7911;a c&#417; quan, t&#7893; ch&#7913;c, ch&#7913;ng minh nh&acirc;n d&acirc;n c&#7911;a b&#7843;n th&acirc;n v&agrave; c&#7911;a ng&#432;&#7901;i &#7911;y th&aacute;c &#273;&#7875; ki&#7875;m tra, &#273;&#7889;i chi&#7871;u<br />\r\n- C&aacute;n b&#7897; tra&#777; k&#7871;t qu&#7843; ki&ecirc;&#777;m tra va&#768; y&ecirc;u c&acirc;&#768;u ng&#432;&#417;&#768;i &#273;&ecirc;&#769;n nh&acirc;&#803;n h&#7897; chi&#7871;u ky&#769; nh&acirc;&#803;n, tr&#7843; h&#7897; chi&#7871;u cho ng&#432;&#417;&#768;i &#273;&ecirc;&#769;n nh&acirc;&#803;n h&#7897; chi&#7871;u.<br />\r\n- Th&#7901;i gian tr&#7843; h&#7897; chi&#7871;u: T&#432;&#768; th&#7913; 2 &#273;&#7871;n th&#7913; 7 ha&#768;ng tu&acirc;&#768;n (nga&#768;y l&ecirc;&#771; nghi&#777;).<br />\r\n* &#272;&#7883;a &#273;i&#7875;m, c&aacute;ch th&#7913;c nh&#7853;n h&#7897; chi&#7871;u qua &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng b&#432;u &#273;i&#7879;n th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n theo h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n c&#7911;a T&#7853;p &#273;o&agrave;n B&#432;u ch&iacute;nh vi&#7877;n th&ocirc;ng Vi&#7879;t Nam.</p>\r\n', '<p>1- Tr&#7921;c ti&#7871;p t&#7841;i tr&#7909; s&#7903; &#272;&#7897;i Qu&#7843;n l&yacute; xu&#7845;t nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh- Ph&ograve;ng PA39- C&ocirc;ng an t&#7881;nh H&#432;ng Y&ecirc;n;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2- Nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i sau &#273;&acirc;y c&oacute; th&#7875; &#7911;y th&aacute;c cho c&#417; quan, t&#7893; ch&#7913;c c&oacute; t&#432; c&aacute;ch ph&aacute;p nh&acirc;n n&#417;i ng&#432;&#7901;i &#273;&oacute; &#273;ang l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c, h&#7885;c t&#7853;p n&#7897;p h&#7891; s&#417; v&agrave; nh&#7853;n k&#7871;t qu&#7843;:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- C&aacute;n b&#7897;, c&ocirc;ng ch&#7913;c, vi&ecirc;n ch&#7913;c &#273;ang l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c trong c&aacute;c c&#417; quan nh&agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c; s&#7929; quan, h&#7841; s&#7929; quan, chi&#7871;n s&#297;, c&ocirc;ng nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n &#273;ang ph&#7909;c v&#7909; trong c&aacute;c &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; Qu&acirc;n &#273;&#7897;i nh&acirc;n d&acirc;n v&agrave; C&ocirc;ng an nh&acirc;n d&acirc;n c&oacute; th&#7875; &#7911;y th&aacute;c cho c&#417; quan, &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; &#273;&oacute;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- C&aacute;n b&#7897;, nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n thu&#7897;c c&aacute;c &#273;o&agrave;n th&#7875;, t&#7893; ch&#7913;c nh&acirc;n d&acirc;n &#7903; Trung &#432;&#417;ng v&agrave; c&#7845;p t&#7881;nh c&oacute; th&#7875; &#7911;y th&aacute;c cho &#273;o&agrave;n th&#7875;, t&#7893; ch&#7913;c &#273;&oacute;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- C&aacute;n b&#7897;, gi&aacute;o vi&ecirc;n, nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n, sinh vi&ecirc;n &#273;ang l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c v&agrave; h&#7885;c t&#7853;p trong c&aacute;c Tr&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#7841;i h&#7885;c, cao &#273;&#7859;ng, trung h&#7885;c chuy&ecirc;n nghi&#7879;p, tr&#432;&#7901;ng d&#7841;y ngh&#7873; c&oacute; th&#7875; &#7911;y th&aacute;c cho tr&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&oacute;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- C&aacute;n b&#7897;, nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n trong c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng ty tr&aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m h&#7919;u h&#7841;n Nh&agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c m&#7897;t th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n, c&ocirc;ng ty c&#7893; ph&#7847;n c&oacute; v&#7889;n Nh&agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c m&agrave; ng&#432;&#7901;i &#273;i&#7873;u h&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng ty do c&#417; quan Nh&agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c ho&#7863;c &#273;o&agrave;n th&#7875;, t&#7893; ch&#7913;c nh&acirc;n d&acirc;n &#7903; Trung &#432;&#417;ng c&#7917; sang c&oacute; th&#7875; &#7911;y th&aacute;c cho c&ocirc;ng ty &#273;&oacute;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Ng&#432;&#7901;i &#273;&atilde; k&yacute; h&#7907;p &#273;&#7891;ng lao &#273;&#7897;ng n&#432;&#7899;c ngo&agrave;i v&#7899;i doanh nghi&#7879;p ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u lao &#273;&#7897;ng &#273;&atilde; c&oacute; gi&#7845;y ph&eacute;p c&#7911;a c&#417; quan qu&#7843;n l&yacute; nh&agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c v&#7873; lao &#273;&#7897;ng v&agrave; &#273;&atilde; k&yacute; h&#7907;p &#273;&#7891;ng cung &#7913;ng lao &#273;&#7897;ng v&#7899;i &#273;&#7889;i t&aacute;c n&#432;&#7899;c ngo&agrave;i c&oacute; th&#7875; &#7911;y th&aacute;c cho doanh nghi&#7879;p &#273;&oacute;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Doanh nghi&#7879;p ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u lao &#273;&#7897;ng ph&#7843;i g&#7917;i h&#7891; s&#417; th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o t&#432; c&aacute;ch ph&aacute;p nh&acirc;n &#273;&#7871;n &#272;&#7897;i Qu&#7843;n l&yacute; xu&#7845;t nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh- Ph&ograve;ng PA39- C&ocirc;ng an t&#7881;nh H&#432;ng Y&ecirc;n tr&#432;&#7899;c khi c&#7917; c&aacute;n b&#7897;, nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n &#273;&#7871;n l&agrave;m th&#7911; t&#7909;c &#273;&#7873; ngh&#7883; c&#7845;p, s&#7917;a &#273;&#7893;i h&#7897; chi&#7871;u cho ng&#432;&#7901;i &#7911;y th&aacute;c &#273;&atilde; k&yacute; h&#7907;p &#273;&#7891;ng &#273;i lao &#273;&#7897;ng n&#432;&#7899;c ngo&agrave;i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3- Th&ocirc;ng quan h&#7879; th&#7889;ng B&#432;u ch&iacute;nh (theo h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n c&#7911;a T&#7853;p &#273;o&agrave;n B&#432;u ch&iacute;nh vi&#7877;n th&ocirc;ng Vi&#7879;t Nam).</p>\r\n', 'C&#225; nh&#226;n', '<p>Kh&ocirc;ng qu&aacute; 08 ng&agrave;y l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c, k&#7875; t&#7915; ng&agrave;y nh&#7853;n &#273;&#7847;y &#273;&#7911; h&#7891; s&#417; theo quy &#273;&#7883;nh.</p>\r\n', '<p>- L&#7879; ph&iacute; b&#7893; sung, s&#7917;a &#273;&#7893;i h&#7897; chi&#7871;u b&#7857;ng 25% l&#7879; ph&iacute; c&#7845;p m&#7899;i ( 50.000 &#273;).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(Th&ocirc;ng t&#432; s&#7889; 66/2009/TT-BTC ng&agrave;y 30/3/2009 c&#7911;a B&#7897; tr&#432;&#7903;ng B&#7897; T&agrave;i ch&iacute;nh ban h&agrave;nh quy &#273;&#7883;nh ch&#7871; &#273;&#7897; thu, n&#7897;p, qu&#7843;n l&yacute; v&agrave; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng l&#7879; ph&iacute; c&#7845;p h&#7897; chi&#7871;u, th&#7883; th&#7921;c, gi&#7845;y t&#7901; v&#7873; nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh, xu&#7845;t c&#7843;nh, qu&aacute; c&#7843;nh v&agrave; c&#432; tr&uacute; t&#7841;i Vi&#7879;t Nam)</p>\r\n', 'Th&#7867; t&#7841;m tr&#250;', 'S&#7917;a &#273;&#7893;i h&#7897; chi&#7871;u ph&#7893; th&#244;ng t&#7841;i C&#244;ng an c&#7845;p t&#7881;nh', 'Sua_doi_ho_chieu_pho_thong_tai_Cong_an_cap_tinh.doc', '<p>- 01 t&#7901; khai theo m&#7851;u quy &#273;&#7883;nh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 04 &#7843;nh m&#7899;i ch&#7909;p, c&#7905; 4x6 cm, m&#7863;t nh&igrave;n th&#7859;ng, &#273;&#7847;u &#273;&#7875; tr&#7847;n, ph&ocirc;ng n&#7873;n m&agrave;u tr&#7855;ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>H&#7891; s&#417; &#273;&#7873; ngh&#7883; s&#7917;a &#273;&#7893;i h&#7897; chi&#7871;u (&#273;i&#7873;u ch&#7881;nh h&#7885; v&agrave; t&ecirc;n, ng&agrave;y th&aacute;ng n&#259;m sinh, n&#417;i sinh, s&#7889; ch&#7913;ng minh nh&acirc;n d&acirc;n trong h&#7897; chi&#7871;u; b&#7893; sung tr&#7867; em v&agrave;o h&#7897; chi&#7871;u c&#7911;a m&#7865; ho&#7863;c cha):</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p &#273;&#7873; ngh&#7883; &#273;i&#7873;u ch&#7881;nh h&#7885; v&agrave; t&ecirc;n, ng&agrave;y th&aacute;ng n&#259;m sinh, n&#417;i sinh, s&#7889; ch&#7913;ng minh nh&acirc;n d&acirc;n th&igrave; n&#7897;p 01 t&#7901; khai theo m&#7851;u quy &#273;&#7883;nh, k&egrave;m b&#7843;n sao gi&#7845;y ch&#7913;ng minh nh&acirc;n d&acirc;n ho&#7863;c gi&#7845;y t&#7901; c&oacute; gi&aacute; tr&#7883; ph&aacute;p l&yacute; ch&#7913;ng minh s&#7921; &#273;i&#7873;u ch&#7881;nh &#273;&oacute;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p b&#7893; sung tr&#7867; em v&agrave;o h&#7897; chi&#7871;u m&#7865; ho&#7863;c cha th&igrave; n&#7897;p th&ecirc;m 04 &#7843;nh c&#7905; 3x4 cm c&#7911;a tr&#7867; em. Vi&#7879;c khai v&agrave; x&aacute;c nh&#7853;n v&agrave;o t&#7901; khai th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n nh&#432; &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i h&#7891; s&#417; c&#7845;p l&#7847;n &#273;&#7847;u.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>H&#7897; chi&#7871;u &#273;&#7873; ngh&#7883; s&#7917;a &#273;&#7893;i c&ograve;n th&#7901;i h&#7841;n &iacute;t nh&#7845;t m&#7897;t n&#259;m.</p>\r\n', '1', '<p>Kh&ocirc;ng</p>\r\n', '<p>- Ngh&#7883; &#273;&#7883;nh s&#7889; 136/2007/N&#272;-CP ng&agrave;y 17/8/2007 c&#7911;a Ch&iacute;nh ph&#7911; v&#7873; xu&#7845;t c&#7843;nh, nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh c&#7911;a c&ocirc;ng d&acirc;n Vi&#7879;t Nam;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Ch&#7881; th&#7883; s&#7889; 29/2007/CT-TTg ng&agrave;y 11/12/2007 c&#7911;a Th&#7911; t&#432;&#7899;ng Ch&iacute;nh ph&#7911; v&#7873; th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n c&#7843;i c&aacute;ch h&agrave;nh ch&iacute;nh trong qu&#7843;n l&yacute; xu&#7845;t c&#7843;nh, nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh c&#7911;a c&aacute;n b&#7897;, c&ocirc;ng ch&#7913;c, c&ocirc;ng d&acirc;n;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Th&ocirc;ng t&#432; s&#7889; 27/2007/TT-BCA(A11) ng&agrave;y 29/11/2007 c&#7911;a B&#7897; tr&#432;&#7903;ng B&#7897; C&ocirc;ng an h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n vi&#7879;c c&#7845;p, s&#7917;a &#273;&#7893;i h&#7897; chi&#7871;u ph&#7893; th&ocirc;ng &#7903; trong n&#432;&#7899;c;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Th&ocirc;ng