(6, 'C&#7845;p gi&#7845;y x&#225;c nh&#7853;n t&#236;nh tr&#7841;ng ti&#7873;n &#225;n (d&#249;ng cho ng&#432;&#7901;i &#273;i l&#224;m vi&#7879;c c&#243; th&#7901;i h&#7841;n &#7903; n&#432;&#7899;c ngo&#224;i).', 1, 0, '<p>a) C&#417; quan c&oacute; th&#7849;m quy&#7873;n quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh: Ph&ograve;ng H&#7891; s&#417; nghi&#7879;p v&#7909;, CA t&#7881;nh H&#432;ng y&ecirc;n.<br />\r\nb) C&#417; quan ho&#7863;c ng&#432;&#7901;i c&oacute; th&#7849;m quy&#7873;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c u&#7927; quy&#7873;n ho&#7863;c ph&acirc;n c&#7845;p th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n (n&#7871;u c&oacute;): kh&ocirc;ng<br />\r\nc) C&#417; quan tr&#7921;c ti&#7871;p th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n TTHC: Ph&ograve;ng H&#7891; s&#417;, CA t&#7881;nh H&#432;ng y&ecirc;n.<br />\r\nc) C&#417; quan ph&#7889;i h&#7907;p (n&#7871;u c&oacute;):</p>\r\n', '<p>- &#272;&#7889;i v&#7899;i c&aacute; nh&acirc;n, t&#7893; ch&#7913;c:<br />\r\n+ &#272;&#7871;n tr&#7909; s&#7903; ti&#7871;p c&ocirc;ng d&acirc;n t&igrave;m hi&#7875;u tr&igrave;nh t&#7921; th&#7911; t&#7909;c, n&#7897;i dung c&aacute;c v&#259;n b&#7843;n h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n &#273;&atilde; ni&ecirc;m y&#7871;t c&ocirc;ng khai, ho&#7863;c qua s&#7921; h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n c&#7911;a c&aacute;n b&#7897; ti&#7871;p d&acirc;n &#273;&#7875; bi&#7871;t r&otilde; th&#7911; t&#7909;c;<br />\r\n+ Vi&#7871;t &#272;&#417;n &#273;&#7873; ngh&#7883; x&aacute;c nh&#7853;n t&igrave;nh tr&#7841;ng ti&#7873;n &aacute;n; xu&#7845;t tr&igrave;nh Gi&#7845;y CMND, s&#7893; &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; H&#7897; kh&#7849;u;<br />\r\n+ Nh&#7853;n k&#7871;t qu&#7843; gi&#7843;i quy&#7871;t v&agrave; n&#7897;p l&#7879; ph&iacute; theo quy &#273;&#7883;nh.<br />\r\n- &#272;&#7889;i v&#7899;i c&#417; quan gi&#7843;i quy&#7871;t th&#7911; t&#7909;c c&#7845;p gi&#7845;y x&aacute;c nh&#7853;n t&igrave;nh tr&#7841;ng ti&#7873;n &aacute;n:<br />\r\n+ H&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n c&aacute; nh&acirc;n, t&#7893; ch&#7913;c v&#7873; tr&igrave;nh t&#7921; th&#7911; t&#7909;c gi&#7843;i quy&#7871;t;<br />\r\n+ Ti&#7871;p nh&#7853;n th&#7911; t&#7909;c;<br />\r\n+ Th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o cho c&aacute; nh&acirc;n, t&#7893; ch&#7913;c v&#7873; th&#7901;i h&#7841;n gi&#7843;i quy&#7871;t v&agrave; tr&#7843; k&#7871;t qu&#7843; (theo quy tr&igrave;nh th&#7911; t&#7909;c &#273;&atilde; ni&ecirc;m y&#7871;t c&ocirc;ng khai);<br />\r\n+ Tr&#7843; k&#7871;t qu&#7843; c&#7845;p gi&#7845;y x&aacute;c nh&#7853;n t&igrave;nh tr&#7841;ng ti&#7873;n &aacute;n cho c&aacute; nh&acirc;n, t&#7893; ch&#7913;c theo th&#7901;i h&#7841;n quy &#273;&#7883;nh</p>\r\n', '<p>- Tr&#7921;c ti&#7871;p n&#7897;p h&#7891; s&#417; v&agrave; nh&#7853;n k&#7871;t qu&#7843; t&#7841;i Ph&ograve;ng PV27 &ndash;CA T&#7881;nh H&#432;ng Y&ecirc;n</p>\r\n', 'C&#225; nh&#226;n', '<p>05 ng&agrave;y l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c.</p>\r\n', '<p>M&#7913;c thu l&#7879; ph&iacute; c&#7845;p gi&#7845;y x&aacute;c nh&#7853;n kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; ti&#7873;n &aacute;n l&agrave; 50.000 (N&#259;m m&#432;&#417;i ngh&igrave;n) &#273;&#7891;ng / l&#7847;n / ng&#432;&#7901;i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(Quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh s&#7889; 146/2000/Q&#272;/BTC c&#7911;a B&#7897; t&agrave;i ch&iacute;nh v&#7873; vi&#7879;c ban h&agrave;nh c&#7845;p l&#7879; ph&iacute; c&#7845;p phi&#7871;u l&yacute; l&#7883;ch t&#432; ph&aacute;p, ng&agrave;y 18/9/2000; Th&ocirc;ng t&#432; s&#7889; 99/2005/TT-BTC, ng&agrave;y 14/11/2005 c &#7911;a B&#7897; t&agrave;i ch&iacute;nh quy &#273;&#7883;nh ch&#7871; &#273;&#7897; thu, n&#7897;p v&agrave; qu&#7843;n l&yacute; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng l&#7879; ph&iacute; c&#7845;p gi&#7845;y x&aacute;c nh&#7853;n kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; ti&#7873;n &aacute;n cho ng &#432;&#7901;i lao &#273;&#7897;ng &#273;i l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c c&oacute; th&#7901;i h&#7841;n t&#7841;i n &#432;&#7899;c ngo&agrave;i.)</p>\r\n', 'Gi&#7845;y x&#225;c nh&#7853;n', 'C&#7845;p gi&#7845;y x&#225;c nh&#7853;n t&#236;nh tr&#7841;ng ti&#7873;n &#225;n (d&#249;ng cho ng&#432;&#7901;i &#273;i l&#224;m vi&#7879;c c&#243; th&#7901;i h&#7841;n &#7903; n&#432;&#7899;c ngo&#224;i).', 'Cap_giay_xac_nhan_tinh_trang_tien_an.doc', '<p>- &#272;&#417;n &#273;&#7873; ngh&#7883; x&aacute;c nh&#7853;n t&igrave;nh tr&#7841;ng ti&#7873;n &aacute;n;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- B&#7843;n sao s&#7893; H&#7897; kh&#7849;u, gi&#7845;y CMND.</p>\r\n', '1', '<p>Kh&ocirc;ng</p>\r\n', '<p>- C&ocirc;ng v&#259;n s&#7889; 68/CP-VX, ng&agrave;y 17/10/2000 c&#7911;a B&#7897; C&ocirc;ng an v&#7873; vi&#7879;c c&#7845;p gi&#7845;y x&aacute;c nh&#7853;n kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; ti&#7873;n &aacute;n cho ng &#432;&#7901;i lao &#273;&#7897;ng &#273;i l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c c&oacute; th&#7901;i h&#7841;n t&#7841;i &#272;&agrave;i Loan. C&oacute; hi&#7879;u l&#7921;c ng&agrave;y 17/10/2000;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- H&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n s&#7889; 1760/2000/BCA(C11) ng&agrave;y 25/10/2000 ng&agrave;y 25/10/2000 c&#7911;a B&#7897; C&ocirc;ng an v&#7873; c&#7845;p ph&aacute;t Gi&#7845;y x&aacute;c nh&#7853;n kh&ocirc;ng ti&#7873;n &aacute;n cho ng&#432;&#7901;i &#273;i l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c c&oacute; th&#7901;i h&#7841;n t&#7841;i &#272;&agrave;i Loan.; Ng&agrave;y c&oacute; hi&#7879;u l&#7921;c: 25/10/2000.</p>\r\n', 'cap-giay-xac-nhan-tinh-trang-tien-an-dung-cho-nguoi-di-lam-viec-co-thoi-han-o-nuoc-ngoai', 4, 3),
(7, 'C&#7845;p l&#7841;i h&#7897; chi&#7871;u ph&#7893; th&#244;ng t&#7841;i C&#244;ng an c&#7845;p t&#7881;nh', 1, 0, '<p>a) C&#417; quan c&oacute; th&#7849;m quy&#7873;n quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh: C&#7909;c Qu&#7843;n l&yacute; xu&#7845;t nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh, B&#7897; C&ocirc;ng an<br />\r\nb) C&#417; quan ho&#7863;c ng&#432;&#7901;i c&oacute; th&#7849;m quy&#7873;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c u&#7927; quy&#7873;n ho&#7863;c ph&acirc;n c&#7845;p th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n (n&#7871;u c&oacute;): Kh&ocirc;ng<br />\r\nc) C&#417; quan tr&#7921;c ti&#7871;p th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n TTHC: t&#7841;i &#272;&#7897;i Qu&#7843;n l&yacute; xu&#7845;t nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh- Ph&ograve;ng PA39- C&ocirc;ng an t&#7881;nh H&#432;ng Y&ecirc;n.<br />\r\nc) C&#417; quan ph&#7889;i h&#7907;p (n&#7871;u c&oacute;): Kh&ocirc;ng</p>\r\n', '<p>B&#432;&#7899;c 1- Chu&#7849;n b&#7883; h&#7891; s&#417; theo quy &#273;&#7883;nh c&#7911;a ph&aacute;p lu&#7853;t<br />\r\nB&#432;&#7899;c 2- N&#7897;p h&#7891; s&#417; &#273;&#7873; ngh&#7883; c&#7845;p h&#7897; chi&#7871;u t&#7841;i B&#7897; ph&#7853;n ti&#7871;p nh&#7853;n v&agrave; tr&#7843; k&#7871;t qu&#7843; t&#7841;i &#272;&#7897;i Qu&#7843;n l&yacute; xu&#7845;t nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh- Ph&ograve;ng PA39- C&ocirc;ng an t&#7881;nh H&#432;ng Y&ecirc;n theo m&#7897;t trong 3 c&aacute;ch sau &#273;&acirc;y:<br />\r\n- Tr&#7921;c ti&#7871;p n&#7897;p h&#7891; s&#417;:<br />\r\nT&#7901; khai kh&ocirc;ng ph&#7843;i x&aacute;c nh&#7853;n c&#7911;a C&ocirc;ng an x&atilde;, ph&#432;&#7901;ng, th&#7883; tr&#7845;n n&#417;i th&#432;&#7901;ng tr&uacute; ho&#7863;c t&#7841;m tr&uacute;. Khi &#273;&#7871;n n&#7897;p h&#7891; s&#417; ph&#7843;i xu&#7845;t tr&igrave;nh ch&#7913;ng minh nh&acirc;n d&acirc;n &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7889;i chi&#7871;u.<br />\r\nRi&ecirc;ng &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p t&#7841;m tr&uacute;, khi &#273;&#7871;n n&#7897;p h&#7891; s&#417; c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i xu&#7845;t tr&igrave;nh &quot;Gi&#7845;y ch&#7913;ng nh&#7853;n t&#7841;m tr&uacute;&quot;; n&#7871;u kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; &quot;Gi&#7845;y ch&#7913;ng nh&#7853;n t&#7841;m tr&uacute;&quot; th&igrave; ph&#7843;i xin x&aacute;c nh&#7853;n c&#7911;a C&ocirc;ng an x&atilde;, ph&#432;&#7901;ng, th&#7883; tr&#7845;n n&#417;i t&#7841;m tr&uacute;.<br />\r\n- &#7910;y th&aacute;c cho c&#417; quan, t&#7893; ch&#7913;c c&oacute; t&#432; c&aacute;ch ph&aacute;p nh&acirc;n n&#7897;p h&#7891; s&#417;:<br />\r\nNg&#432;&#7901;i &#7911;y th&aacute;c khai v&agrave; k&yacute; t&ecirc;n v&agrave;o t&#7901; khai &#273;&#7873; ngh&#7883; c&#7845;p, s&#7917;a &#273;&#7893;i h&#7897; chi&#7871;u theo m&#7851;u quy &#273;&#7883;nh, c&oacute; d&#7845;u gi&aacute;p lai &#7843;nh v&agrave; x&aacute;c nh&#7853;n c&#7911;a Th&#7911; tr&#432;&#7903;ng c&#417; quan, t&#7893; ch&#7913;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#7911;y th&aacute;c.<br />\r\nC&#417; quan, t&#7893; ch&#7913;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#7911;y th&aacute;c c&oacute; c&ocirc;ng v&#259;n g&#7917;i C&ocirc;ng an t&#7881;nh, &#273;&#7873; ngh&#7883; gi&#7843;i quy&#7871;t. N&#7871;u &#273;&#7873; ngh&#7883; gi&#7843;i quy&#7871;t cho nhi&#7873;u ng&#432;&#7901;i th&igrave; ph&#7843;i k&egrave;m danh s&aacute;ch nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i &#7911;y th&aacute;c, c&oacute; ch&#7919; k&yacute;, &#273;&oacute;ng d&#7845;u c&#7911;a Th&#7911; tr&#432;&#7903;ng c&#417; quan, t&#7893; ch&#7913;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#7911;y th&aacute;c.<br />\r\nC&aacute;n b&#7897;, nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n c&#7911;a c&#417; quan, t&#7893; ch&#7913;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#7911;y th&aacute;c khi n&#7897;p h&#7891; s&#417; &#273;&#7873; ngh&#7883; c&#7845;p, s&#7917;a &#273;&#7893;i h&#7897; chi&#7871;u c&#7911;a ng&#432;&#7901;i &#7911;y th&aacute;c ph&#7843;i xu&#7845;t tr&igrave;nh gi&#7845;y gi&#7899;i thi&#7879;u c&#7911;a c&#417; quan, t&#7893; ch&#7913;c, ch&#7913;ng minh nh&acirc;n d&acirc;n c&#7911;a b&#7843;n th&acirc;n v&agrave; c&#7911;a ng&#432;&#7901;i &#7911;y th&aacute;c &#273;&#7875; ki&#7875;m tra, &#273;&#7889;i chi&#7871;u.<br />\r\n- G&#7917;i h&#7891; s&#417; v&agrave; &#273;&#7873; ngh&#7883; nh&#7853;n k&#7871;t qu&#7843; qua &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng b&#432;u &#273;i&#7879;n:<br />\r\nT&#7901; khai ph&#7843;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c C&ocirc;ng an x&atilde;, ph&#432;&#7901;ng, th&#7883; tr&#7845;n n&#417;i th&#432;&#7901;ng tr&uacute; ho&#7863;c t&#7841;m tr&uacute; x&aacute;c nh&#7853;n v&agrave; &#273;&oacute;ng d&#7845;u gi&aacute;p lai &#7843;nh k&egrave;m theo b&#7843;n photocopy ch&#7913;ng minh nh&acirc;n d&acirc;n.<br />\r\n&#272;&#7883;a &#273;i&#7875;m, c&aacute;ch th&#7913;c g&#7917;i h&#7891; s&#417; qua &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng b&#432;u &#273;i&#7879;n th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n theo h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n c&#7911;a T&#7853;p &#273;o&agrave;n B&#432;u ch&iacute;nh vi&#7877;n th&ocirc;ng Vi&#7879;t Nam.<br />\r\n* C&aacute;n b&#7897; qu&#7843;n l&yacute; xu&#7845;t nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh ti&ecirc;&#769;p nh&acirc;&#803;n h&ocirc;&#768; s&#417; ki&ecirc;&#777;m tra ti&#769;nh pha&#769;p ly&#769; va&#768; n&ocirc;&#803;i dung h&ocirc;&#768; s&#417;:<br />\r\n- Tr&#432;&#417;&#768;ng h&#417;&#803;p h&ocirc;&#768; s&#417; &#273;a&#771; &#273;&acirc;&#768;y &#273;u&#777;, h&#417;&#803;p l&ecirc;&#803; thi&#768; vi&ecirc;&#769;t gi&acirc;&#769;y bi&ecirc;n nh&#7853;n trao cho ng&#432;&#417;&#768;i n&ocirc;&#803;p v&agrave; y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u n&#7897;p l&#7879; ph&iacute; cho c&aacute;n b&#7897; thu l&#7879; ph&iacute;. C&aacute;n b&#7897; thu l&#7879; ph&iacute; nh&#7853;n ti&#7873;n, vi&#7871;t bi&ecirc;n lai thu ti&#7873;n v&agrave; giao gi&#7845;y bi&ecirc;n nh&#7853;n c&ugrave;ng bi&ecirc;n lai thu ti&#7873;n cho ng&#432;&#7901;i n&#7897;p h&#7891; s&#417;.<br />\r\n- Tr&#432;&#417;&#768;ng h&#417;&#803;p h&ocirc;&#768; s&#417; thi&ecirc;&#769;u, ho&#259;&#803;c kh&ocirc;ng h&#417;&#803;p l&ecirc;&#803; thi&#768; c&aacute;n b&#7897; ti&ecirc;&#769;p nh&acirc;&#803;n h&ocirc;&#768; s&#417; h&#432;&#417;&#769;ng d&acirc;&#771;n &#273;&ecirc;&#777; ng&#432;&#417;&#768;i &#273;&ecirc;&#769;n n&ocirc;&#803;p h&ocirc;&#768; s&#417; la&#768;m la&#803;i cho ki&#803;p th&#417;&#768;i<br />\r\n* Th&#417;&#768;i gian ti&ecirc;&#769;p nh&acirc;&#803;n h&ocirc;&#768; s&#417;: T&#432;&#768; th&#7913; 2 &#273;&#7871;n th&#7913; 7 ha&#768;ng tu&acirc;&#768;n (nga&#768;y l&ecirc;&#771; nghi&#777;).<br />\r\nB&#432;&#7899;c 3- Nh&#7853;n h&#7897; chi&#7871;u t&#7841;i t&#7841;i B&#7897; ph&#7853;n ti&#7871;p nh&#7853;n v&agrave; tr&#7843; k&#7871;t qu&#7843; t&#7841;i &#272;&#7897;i Qu&#7843;n l&yacute; xu&#7845;t nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh- Ph&ograve;ng PA39- C&ocirc;ng an t&#7881;nh H&#432;ng Y&ecirc;n:<br />\r\n- Ng&#432;&#7901;i tr&#7921;c ti&#7871;p nh&#7853;n k&#7871;t qu&#7843; &#273;&#432;a gi&#7845;y bi&ecirc;n nh&#7853;n, bi&ecirc;n lai thu ti&#7873;n v&agrave; xu&#7845;t tr&igrave;nh ch&#7913;ng minh nh&acirc;n d&acirc;n &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7889;i chi&#7871;u. C&aacute;n b&#7897;, nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n c&#7911;a c&#417; quan, t&#7893; ch&#7913;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#7911;y th&aacute;c khi nh&#7853;n h&#7897; chi&#7871;u c&#7911;a ng&#432;&#7901;i &#7911;y th&aacute;c ph&#7843;i &#273;&#432;a gi&#7845;y bi&ecirc;n nh&#7853;n, xu&#7845;t tr&igrave;nh gi&#7845;y gi&#7899;i thi&#7879;u c&#7911;a c&#417; quan, t&#7893; ch&#7913;c, ch&#7913;ng minh nh&acirc;n d&acirc;n c&#7911;a b&#7843;n th&acirc;n v&agrave; c&#7911;a ng&#432;&#7901;i &#7911;y th&aacute;c &#273;&#7875; ki&#7875;m tra, &#273;&#7889;i chi&#7871;u<br />\r\n- C&aacute;n b&#7897; tra&#777; k&#7871;t qu&#7843; ki&ecirc;&#777;m tra va&#768; y&ecirc;u c&acirc;&#768;u ng&#432;&#417;&#768;i &#273;&ecirc;&#769;n nh&acirc;&#803;n h&#7897; chi&#7871;u ky&#769; nh&acirc;&#803;n, tr&#7843; h&#7897; chi&#7871;u cho ng&#432;&#417;&#768;i &#273;&ecirc;&#769;n nh&acirc;&#803;n h&#7897; chi&#7871;u.<br />\r\n- Th&#7901;i gian tr&#7843; h&#7897; chi&#7871;u: T&#432;&#768; th&#7913; 2 &#273;&#7871;n th&#7913; 7 ha&#768;ng tu&acirc;&#768;n (nga&#768;y l&ecirc;&#771; nghi&#777;).<br />\r\n* &#272;&#7883;a &#273;i&#7875;m, c&aacute;ch th&#7913;c nh&#7853;n h&#7897; chi&#7871;u qua &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng b&#432;u &#273;i&#7879;n th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n theo h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n c&#7911;a T&#7853;p &#273;o&agrave;n B&#432;u ch&iacute;nh vi&#7877;n th&ocirc;ng Vi&#7879;t Nam.</p>\r\n', '<p>1- Tr&#7921;c ti&#7871;p t&#7841;i tr&#7909; s&#7903; &#272;&#7897;i Qu&#7843;n l&yacute; xu&#7845;t nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh- Ph&ograve;ng PA39- C&ocirc;ng an t&#7881;nh H&#432;ng Y&ecirc;n;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2- Nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i sau &#273;&acirc;y c&oacute; th&#7875; &#7911;y th&aacute;c cho c&#417; quan, t&#7893; ch&#7913;c c&oacute; t&#432; c&aacute;ch ph&aacute;p nh&acirc;n n&#417;i ng&#432;&#7901;i &#273;&oacute; &#273;ang l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c, h&#7885;c t&#7853;p n&#7897;p h&#7891; s&#417; v&agrave; nh&#7853;n k&#7871;t qu&#7843;:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- C&aacute;n b&#7897;, c&ocirc;ng ch&#7913;c, vi&ecirc;n ch&#7913;c &#273;ang l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c trong c&aacute;c c&#417; quan nh&agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c; s&#7929; quan, h&#7841; s&#7929; quan, chi&#7871;n s&#297;, c&ocirc;ng nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n &#273;ang ph&#7909;c v&#7909; trong c&aacute;c &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; Qu&acirc;n &#273;&#7897;i nh&acirc;n d&acirc;n v&agrave; C&ocirc;ng an nh&acirc;n d&acirc;n c&oacute; th&#7875; &#7911;y th&aacute;c cho c&#417; quan, &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; &#273;&oacute;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- C&aacute;n b&#7897;, nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n thu&#7897;c c&aacute;c &#273;o&agrave;n th&#7875;, t&#7893; ch&#7913;c nh&acirc;n d&acirc;n &#7903; Trung &#432;&#417;ng v&agrave; c&#7845;p t&#7881;nh c&oacute; th&#7875; &#7911;y th&aacute;c cho &#273;o&agrave;n th&#7875;, t&#7893; ch&#7913;c &#273;&oacute;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- C&aacute;n b&#7897;, gi&aacute;o vi&ecirc;n, nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n, sinh vi&ecirc;n &#273;ang l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c v&agrave; h&#7885;c t&#7853;p trong c&aacute;c Tr&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#7841;i h&#7885;c, cao &#273;&#7859;ng, trung h&#7885;c chuy&ecirc;n nghi&#7879;p, tr&#432;&#7901;ng d&#7841;y ngh&#7873; c&oacute; th&#7875; &#7911;y th&aacute;c cho tr&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&oacute;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- C&aacute;n b&#7897;, nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n trong c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng ty tr&aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m h&#7919;u h&#7841;n Nh&agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c m&#7897;t th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n, c&ocirc;ng ty c&#7893; ph&#7847;n c&oacute; v&#7889;n Nh&agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c m&agrave; ng&#432;&#7901;i &#273;i&#7873;u h&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng ty do c&#417; quan Nh&agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c ho&#7863;c &#273;o&agrave;n th&#7875;, t&#7893; ch&#7913;c nh&acirc;n d&acirc;n &#7903; Trung &#432;&#417;ng c&#7917; sang c&oacute; th&#7875; &#7911;y th&aacute;c cho c&ocirc;ng ty &#273;&oacute;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Ng&#432;&#7901;i &#273;&atilde; k&yacute; h&#7907;p &#273;&#7891;ng lao &#273;&#7897;ng n&#432;&#7899;c ngo&agrave;i v&#7899;i doanh nghi&#7879;p ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u lao &#273;&#7897;ng &#273;&atilde; c&oacute; gi&#7845;y ph&eacute;p c&#7911;a c&#417; quan qu&#7843;n l&yacute; nh&agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c v&#7873; lao &#273;&#7897;ng v&agrave; &#273;&atilde; k&yacute; h&#7907;p &#273;&#7891;ng cung &#7913;ng lao &#273;&#7897;ng v&#7899;i &#273;&#7889;i t&aacute;c n&#432;&#7899;c ngo&agrave;i c&oacute; th&#7875; &#7911;y th&aacute;c cho doanh nghi&#7879;p &#273;&oacute;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Doanh nghi&#7879;p ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u lao &#273;&#7897;ng ph&#7843;i g&#7917;i h&#7891; s&#417; th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o t&#432; c&aacute;ch ph&aacute;p nh&acirc;n &#273;&#7871;n &#272;&#7897;i Qu&#7843;n l&yacute; xu&#7845;t nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh- Ph&ograve;ng PA39- C&ocirc;ng an t&#7881;nh H&#432;ng Y&ecirc;n tr&#432;&#7899;c khi c&#7917; c&aacute;n b&#7897;, nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n &#273;&#7871;n l&agrave;m th&#7911; t&#7909;c &#273;&#7873; ngh&#7883; c&#7845;p, s&#7917;a &#273;&#7893;i h&#7897; chi&#7871;u cho ng&#432;&#7901;i &#7911;y th&aacute;c &#273;&atilde; k&yacute; h&#7907;p &#273;&#7891;ng &#273;i lao &#273;&#7897;ng n&#432;&#7899;c ngo&agrave;i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3- Th&ocirc;ng quan h&#7879; th&#7889;ng B&#432;u ch&iacute;nh (theo h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n c&#7911;a T&#7853;p &#273;o&agrave;n B&#432;u ch&iacute;nh vi&#7877;n th&ocirc;ng Vi&#7879;t Nam).</p>\r\n', 'C&#225; nh&#226;n', '<p>Kh&ocirc;ng qu&aacute; 08 ng&agrave;y l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c, k&#7875; t&#7915; ng&agrave;y nh&#7853;n &#273;&#7847;y &#273;&#7911; h&#7891; s&#417; theo quy &#273;&#7883;nh.</p>\r\n', '<p>L&#7879; ph&iacute; c&#7845;p l&#7841;i do b&#7883; h&#432; h&#7887;ng ho&#7863;c b&#7883; m&#7845;t: 400.000 &#273;&#7891;ng (Th&ocirc;ng t&#432; s&#7889; 66/2009/TT-BTC ng&agrave;y 30/3/2009 c&#7911;a B&#7897; tr&#432;&#7903;ng B&#7897; T&agrave;i ch&iacute;nh ban h&agrave;nh quy &#273;&#7883;nh ch&#7871; &#273;&#7897; thu, n&#7897;p, qu&#7843;n l&yacute; v&agrave; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng l&#7879; ph&iacute; c&#7845;p h&#7897; chi&#7871;u, th&#7883; th&#7921;c, gi&#7845;y t&#7901; v&#7873; nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh, xu&#7845;t c&#7843;nh, qu&aacute; c&#7843;nh v&agrave; c&#432; tr&uacute; t&#7841;i Vi&#7879;t Nam)</p>\r\n', 'H&#7897; chi&#7871;u ph&#7893; th&#244;ng', 'C&#7845;p l&#7841;i h&#7897; chi&#7871;u ph&#7893; th&#244;ng t&#7841;i C&#244;ng an c&#7845;p t&#7881;nh', 'Cap_lai_ho_chieu_pho_thong_tai_Cong_an_cap_tinh.doc', '<p>- 01 t&#7901; khai theo m&#7851;u quy &#273;&#7883;nh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 04 &#7843;nh m&#7899;i ch&#7909;p, c&#7905; 4x6 cm, m&#7863;t nh&igrave;n th&#7859;ng, &#273;&#7847;u &#273;&#7875; tr&#7847;n, ph&ocirc;ng n&#7873;n m&agrave;u tr&#7855;ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- C&#7845;p l&#7841;i h&#7897; chi&#7871;u (h&#7897; chi&#7871;u b&#7883; m&#7845;t; b&#7883; h&#432; h&#7887;ng; c&ograve;n th&#7901;i h&#7841;n d&#432;&#7899;i 30 ng&agrave;y ho&#7863;c &#273;&atilde; h&#7871;t th&#7901;i h&#7841;n; t&aacute;ch tr&#7867; em trong h&#7897; chi&#7871;u c&#7911;a m&#7865; ho&#7863;c cha), ngo&agrave;i quy &#273;&#7883;nh nh&#432; h&#7891; s&#417; c&#7845;p l&#7847;n &#273;&#7847;u, ph&#7843;i b&#7893; sung gi&#7845;y t&#7901; c&aacute;c tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p sau:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p m&#7845;t h&#7897; chi&#7871;u th&igrave; n&#7897;p gi&#7845;y &#273;&atilde; tr&igrave;nh b&aacute;o vi&#7879;c m&#7845;t h&#7897; chi&#7871;u theo quy &#273;&#7883;nh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p h&#7897; chi&#7871;u b&#7883; h&#432; h&#7887;ng ho&#7863;c h&#7897; chi&#7871;u c&ograve;n th&#7901;i h&#7841;n d&#432;&#7899;i 30 ng&agrave;y th&igrave; n&#7897;p l&#7841;i h&#7897; chi&#7871;u &#273;&oacute;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p t&aacute;ch tr&#7867; em trong h&#7897; chi&#7871;u c&#7911;a m&#7865; ho&#7863;c cha th&igrave; n&#7897;p h&#7897; chi&#7871;u, 01 t&#7901; khai theo m&#7851;u quy &#273;&#7883;nh v&agrave; 02 &#7843;nh c&#7911;a m&#7865; ho&#7863;c cha &#273;&#7875; c&#7845;p l&#7841;i h&#7897; chi&#7871;u; n&#7897;p 01 t&#7901; khai theo m&#7851;u quy &#273;&#7883;nh v&agrave; 02 &#7843;nh c&#7911;a tr&#7867; em &#273;&#7875; c&#7845;p ri&ecirc;ng h&#7897; chi&#7871;u cho tr&#7867; em &#273;&oacute; (t&#7901; khai do m&#7865; ho&#7863;c cha khai, k&yacute; t&ecirc;n).</p>\r\n', '1', '<p>Kh&ocirc;ng</p>\r\n', '<p>- Ngh&#7883; &#273;&#7883;nh s&#7889; 136/2007/N&#272;-CP ng&agrave;y 17/8/2007 c&#7911;a Ch&iacute;nh ph&#7911; v&#7873; xu&#7845;t c&#7843;nh, nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh c&#7911;a c&ocirc;ng d&acirc;n Vi&#7879;t Nam;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Ch&#7881; th&#7883; s&#7889; 29/2007/CT-TTg ng&agrave;y 11/12/2007 c&#7911;a Th&#7911; t&#432;&#7899;ng Ch&iacute;nh ph&#7911; v&#7873; th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n c&#7843;i c&aacute;ch h&agrave;nh ch&iacute;nh trong qu&#7843;n l&yacute; xu&#7845;t c&#7843;nh, nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh c&#7911;a c&aacute;n b&#7897;, c&ocirc;ng ch&#7913;c, c&ocirc;ng d&acirc;n;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Th&ocirc;ng t&#432; s&#7889; 27/2007/TT-BCA(A11) ng&agrave;y 29/11/2007 c&#7911;a B&#7897; tr&#432;&#7903;ng B&#7897; C&ocirc;ng an h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n vi&#7879;c c&#7845;p, s&#7917;a &#273;&#7893;i h&#7897; chi&#7871;u ph&#7