irc;&#768; s&#417;:<br />\r\n- Tr&#432;&#417;&#768;ng h&#417;&#803;p h&ocirc;&#768; s&#417; &#273;a&#771; &#273;&acirc;&#768;y &#273;u&#777;, h&#417;&#803;p l&ecirc;&#803; thi&#768; vi&ecirc;&#769;t gi&acirc;&#769;y bi&ecirc;n nh&#7853;n trao cho ng&#432;&#417;&#768;i n&ocirc;&#803;p h&#7891; s&#417;.<br />\r\n- Tr&#432;&#417;&#768;ng h&#417;&#803;p h&ocirc;&#768; s&#417; thi&ecirc;&#769;u, ho&#259;&#803;c kh&ocirc;ng h&#417;&#803;p l&ecirc;&#803; thi&#768; c&aacute;n b&#7897; ti&ecirc;&#769;p nh&acirc;&#803;n h&ocirc;&#768; s&#417; h&#432;&#417;&#769;ng d&acirc;&#771;n &#273;&ecirc;&#777; ng&#432;&#417;&#768;i &#273;&ecirc;&#769;n n&ocirc;&#803;p h&ocirc;&#768; s&#417; la&#768;m la&#803;i cho ki&#803;p th&#417;&#768;i<br />\r\n* Th&#417;&#768;i gian ti&ecirc;&#769;p nh&acirc;&#803;n h&ocirc;&#768; s&#417;: T&#432;&#768; th&#7913; 2 &#273;&#7871;n th&#7913; 7 ha&#768;ng tu&acirc;&#768;n (nga&#768;y l&ecirc;&#771; nghi&#777;).<br />\r\nB&#432;&#7899;c 3- Nh&#7853;n th&#7867; t&#7841;m tr&uacute; t&#7841;i B&#7897; ph&#7853;n ti&#7871;p nh&#7853;n v&agrave; tr&#7843; k&#7871;t qu&#7843; t&#7841;i &#272;&#7897;i Qu&#7843;n l&yacute; xu&#7845;t nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh- Ph&ograve;ng PA39- C&ocirc;ng an t&#7881;nh H&#432;ng Y&ecirc;n:<br />\r\n- Ng&#432;&#7901;i nh&#7853;n &#273;&#432;a gi&#7845;y bi&ecirc;n nh&#7853;n, bi&ecirc;n lai thu ti&#7873;n &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7889;i chi&#7871;u. N&#7897;p l&#7879; ph&iacute; cho c&aacute;n b&#7897; thu l&#7879; ph&iacute;. C&aacute;n b&#7897; thu l&#7879; ph&iacute; nh&#7853;n ti&#7873;n, vi&#7871;t bi&ecirc;n lai thu ti&#7873;n v&agrave; giao bi&ecirc;n lai thu ti&#7873;n cho ng&#432;&#7901;i n&#7897;p h&#7891; s&#417;. C&aacute;n b&#7897; tra&#777; k&#7871;t qu&#7843; ki&ecirc;&#777;m tra va&#768; y&ecirc;u c&acirc;&#768;u ky&#769; nh&acirc;&#803;n, tr&#7843; th&#7867; t&#7841;m tr&uacute; cho ng&#432;&#417;&#768;i &#273;&ecirc;&#769;n nh&acirc;&#803;n k&#7871;t qu&#7843;.<br />\r\n*Th&#7901;i gian tr&#7843; k&#7871;t qu&#7843;: T&#432;&#768; th&#7913; 2 &#273;&#7871;n th&#7913; 7 ha&#768;ng tu&acirc;&#768;n (nga&#768;y l&ecirc;&#771; nghi&#777;).</p>\r\n', '<p>Tr&#7921;c ti&#7871;p t&#7841;i tr&#7909; s&#7903; &#272;&#7897;i Qu&#7843;n l&yacute; xu&#7845;t nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh- Ph&ograve;ng PA39- C&ocirc;ng an t&#7881;nh H&#432;ng Y&ecirc;n</p>\r\n', '	  C&#225; nh&#226;n', '<p>Kh&ocirc;ng qu&aacute; 05 ng&agrave;y l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c k&#7875; t&#7915; ng&agrave;y nh&#7853;n &#273;&#7911; h&#7891; s&#417;.</p>\r\n', '<p>C&#7845;p &#273;&#7893;i do gia h&#7841;n ch&#7913;ng nh&#7853;n t&#7841;m tr&uacute;: 10 USD</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(Th&ocirc;ng t&#432; s&#7889; 66/2009/TT-BTC ng&agrave;y 30/3/2009 c&#7911;a B&#7897; tr&#432;&#7903;ng B&#7897; T&agrave;i ch&iacute;nh ban h&agrave;nh quy &#273;&#7883;nh ch&#7871; &#273;&#7897; thu, n&#7897;p, qu&#7843;n l&yacute; v&agrave; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng l&#7879; ph&iacute; c&#7845;p h&#7897; chi&#7871;u, th&#7883; th&#7921;c, gi&#7845;y t&#7901; v&#7873; nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh, xu&#7845;t c&#7843;nh, qu&aacute; c&#7843;nh v&agrave; c&#432; tr&uacute; t&#7841;i Vi&#7879;t Nam)</p>\r\n', 'Th&#7867; t&#7841;m tr&#250;', 'C&#7845;p, gia h&#7841;n ch&#7913;ng nh&#7853;n t&#7841;m tr&#250;; c&#7845;p, b&#7893; sung, s&#7917;a &#273;&#7893;i th&#7883; th&#7921;c cho ng&#432;&#7901;i n&#432;&#7899;c ngo&#224;i ', 'Cap_doi_the_tam_tru_cho_nguoi_nuoc_ngoai_tai_Viet_Nam_tai_Cong_an_cap_tinh.doc', '<p>- V&#259;n b&#7843;n &#273;&#7873; ngh&#7883; c&#7911;a c&#417; quan, t&#7893; ch&#7913;c, c&aacute; nh&acirc;n m&#7901;i, b&#7843;o l&atilde;nh;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 01 t&#7901; khai v&#7873; th&ocirc;ng tin v&#7873; ng&#432;&#7901;i n&#432;&#7899;c ngo&agrave;i xin t&#7841;m tr&uacute;, c&oacute; d&aacute;n &#7843;nh v&agrave; &#273;&oacute;ng d&#7845;u gi&aacute;p lai c&#7911;a c&#417; quan, t&#7893; ch&#7913;c;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 02 &#7843;nh c&#7905; 3 x4 cm;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 01 b&#7843;n ch&#7909;p h&#7897; chi&#7871;u, th&#7883; th&#7921;c c&ograve;n gi&aacute; tr&#7883;, phi&#7871;u xu&#7845;t nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh (mang b&#7843;n ch&iacute;nh &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7889;i chi&#7871;u);</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- 01 b&#7843;n sao ho&#7863;c b&#7843;n pho to (mang b&#7843;n ch&iacute;nh &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7889;i chi&#7871;u) gi&#7845;y t&#7901; ch&#7913;ng minh m&#7909;c &#273;&iacute;ch &#7903; l&#7841;i Vi&#7879;t Nam (tu&#7923; tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p c&#7909; th&#7875; n&#7897;p gi&#7845;y t&#7901; th&iacute;ch h&#7907;p: Gi&#7845;y ph&eacute;p &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;, gi&#7845;y ph&eacute;p th&agrave;nh l&#7853;p doanh nghi&#7879;p, gi&#7845;y ph&eacute;p lao &#273;&#7897;ng, gi&#7845;y x&aacute;c nh&#7853;n th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n h&#7897;i &#273;&#7891;ng qu&#7843;n tr&#7883;, gi&#7845;y ph&eacute;p th&agrave;nh l&#7853;p v&#259;n ph&ograve;ng &#273;&#7841;i di&#7879;n, gi&#7845;y &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; k&#7871;t h&ocirc;n, khai sinh...).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Ngo&agrave;i c&aacute;c lo&#7841;i gi&#7845;y t&#7901; nh&#432; c&#7845;p m&#7899;i c&ograve;n ph&#7843;i n&#7897;p k&egrave;m th&#7867; t&#7841;m tr&uacute; c&#361;. Ri&ecirc;ng tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p chuy&#7875;n ngang gi&aacute; tr&#7883; th&#7867; c&#361; sang th&#7867; m&#7899;i do &#273;&#7893;i s&#7889; h&#7897; chi&#7871;u; ng&#432;&#7901;i &#273;i theo (v&#7907;, con&hellip;) &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&#7845;p th&#7867; t&#7841;m tr&uacute; th&igrave; kh&ocirc;ng ph&#7843;i n&#7897;p gi&#7845;y t&#7901; ch&#7913;ng minh m&#7909;c &#273;&iacute;ch &#7903; l&#7841;i Vi&#7879;t Nam.</p>\r\n', '1', '<p>- C&oacute; th&#7901;i gian t&#7841;m tr&uacute; t&#7841;i Vi&#7879;t Nam t&#7915; 01 n&#259;m tr&#7903; l&ecirc;n;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- H&#7897; chi&#7871;u c&ograve;n th&#7901;i h&#7841;n t&#7915; 01 n&#259;m tr&#7903; l&ecirc;n.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(Ph&aacute;p l&#7879;nh s&#7889; 24/2000/PL-UBTVQH10 ng&agrave;y 28/4/2000 v&#7873; nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh, xu&#7845;t c&#7843;nh, c&#432; tr&uacute; c&#7911;a ng&#432;&#7901;i n&#432;&#7899;c ngo&agrave;i t&#7841;i Vi&#7879;t Nam)</p>\r\n', '<p>- Ph&aacute;p l&#7879;nh s&#7889; 24/2000/PL-UBTVQH10 ng&agrave;y 28/4/2000 v&#7873; nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh, xu&#7845;t c&#7843;nh, c&#432; tr&uacute; c&#7911;a ng&#432;&#7901;i n&#432;&#7899;c ngo&agrave;i t&#7841;i Vi&#7879;t Nam;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Ngh&#7883; &#273;&#7883;nh s&#7889; 21/2001/N&#272;-CP ng&agrave;y 28/5/2001 c&#7911;a Ch&iacute;nh ph&#7911; quy &#273;&#7883;nh chi ti&#7871;t thi h&agrave;nh Ph&aacute;p l&#7879;nh Nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh, xu&#7845;t c&#7843;nh, c&#432; tr&uacute; c&#7911;a ng&#432;&#7901;i n&#432;&#7899;c ngo&agrave;i t&#7841;i Vi&#7879;t Nam;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Th&ocirc;ng t&#432; s&#7889; 66/2009/TT-BTC ng&agrave;y 30/3/2009 c&#7911;a B&#7897; tr&#432;&#7903;ng B&#7897; T&agrave;i ch&iacute;nh ban h&agrave;nh quy &#273;&#7883;nh ch&#7871; &#273;&#7897; thu, n&#7897;p, qu&#7843;n l&yacute; v&agrave; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng l&#7879; ph&iacute; c&#7845;p h&#7897; chi&#7871;u, th&#7883; th&#7921;c, gi&#7845;y t&#7901; v&#7873; nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh, xu&#7845;t c&#7843;nh, qu&aacute; c&#7843;nh v&agrave; c&#432; tr&uacute; t&#7841;i Vi&#7879;t Nam;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Th&ocirc;ng t&#432; li&ecirc;n t&#7883;ch s&#7889; 04/2002/TTLT-BCA-BNG ng&agrave;y 29/01/2002 h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n Ngh&#7883; &#273;&#7883;nh s&#7889; 21/2001/N&#272;-CP ng&agrave;y 28/5/2001 c&#7911;a Ch&iacute;nh ph&#7911; quy &#273;&#7883;nh chi ti&#7871;t thi h&agrave;nh Ph&aacute;p l&#7879;nh Nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh, xu&#7845;t c&#7843;nh, c&#432; tr&uacute; c&#7911;a ng&#432;&#7901;i n&#432;&#7899;c ngo&agrave;i t&#7841;i Vi&#7879;t Nam;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Th&ocirc;ng t&#432; li&ecirc;n t&#7883;ch s&#7889; 01/2007/TTLT-BCA-BNG ng&agrave;y 30/01/2007 s&#7917;a &#273;&#7893;i b&#7893; sung m&#7897;t s&#7889; &#273;i&#7873;u c&#7911;a Th&ocirc;ng t&#432; li&ecirc;n t&#7883;ch s&#7889; 04/2002/TTLT-BCA-BNG ng&agrave;y 29/01/2002.</p>\r\n', 'cap-gia-han-chung-nhan-tam-tru-cap-bo-sung-sua-doi-thi-thuc-cho-nguoi-nuoc-ngoai', 4, 3);

